If the genre of music is something you like, then the music is offering you some advice. If the genre of music you hear in your dream is something you hate, then it means that you are refusing or rejecting some advice.

context: To see or open a music box in your dream
meaning: represents the things that you treasure and hold dear to your heart. Consider the melody of the music box and what is inside the music box. If the music box is broken, then it means that you are experiencing some heartache.

context: To hear a music box in your dream
meaning: indicates a past memory.

context: To see musical notes in your dream
meaning: represent harmony or disharmony in your waking life, depending on whether the musical note was a sharp note or flat note. The dream may also be a pun on a note or message from your subconscious.

context: To watch a music video in your dream
meaning: suggests that you need to interject more excitement and thrill into your life. The dream may serve as a soundtrack of your waking life. Consider the music and imagery of the video and how it parallels your waking life.

context: To dream that you are making or you are in a music video
meaning: suggests that you need to be more expressive and imaginative. Consider the type of video you are in.

context: To dream that you are watching a musical
meaning: indicates that you need to be careful not to get carried away by your emotions.

context: To dream that you are playing musical chairs
meaning: signifies instability in some area of your life. You are feeling uneasy about your position or about some decision you made.

context: To see musical instruments in your dream
meaning: indicate the expectation of fun and pleasures. You are focused on enjoying life and all that it has to offer. The dream also represents your talents and your ability to communicate with others. Certain musical instruments are symbolic of sexual organs and thus point to your sexuality. If you play a musical instrument in your waking life, then the dream may serve as a rehearsal to improve your technique.

context: If you are not a musician in your waking life, but dream that you are one,
meaning: then it implies that you need to be more expressive about your feelings.

context: To see a dead musician in your dream
meaning: suggests that you are no longer able to express yourself in the same way as you did in the past.

context: To smell musk in your dream
meaning: denotes that you will find joy in situations where you least expect it.

context: To see a muskox in your dream
meaning: refers to a relaxed attitude. You don't let trivial things bother you and tend to go with the flow. You are able to handle whatever issues or problems that come your way.

context: To see mussels in your dream
meaning: indicate that you are closing yourself off and isolating yourself from others. Ask yourself why you are shutting others out. The dream may also be a pun on "muscles".

context: To dream that you have a mustache when you don't really have one
meaning: signifies that you are hiding an aspect of yourself. You are putting on a disguise or showing a different aspect of your personality. If you are a woman and dream that you have a mustache, then it indicates that you are expressing your power through your words and your verbal expression. If you dream that you or someone is wearing a fake mustache, then it indicates that you are trying to draw attention away from a minor issue or problem.

context: To dream that you shave off your mustache
meaning: denotes that you are revealing your true self. You no longer have to hide under some disguise or some shield. Alternatively, the dream means that you are trying to reestablish your reputation, by renouncing your previous activities.

context: Dreaming that everyone has a mustache
meaning: indicates that you are suspicious or untrusting of others.

context: To see a mustang in your dream
meaning: represents aggression, wildness, lust and untamed sexuality.

context: To dream that you are a mutant
meaning: represents undeveloped aspects of yourself that you are ignoring or refusing to confront. Alternatively, to dream that you are mutant means that you need to look at things from a different perspective. There is something in your life that you need to drastically change.

context: To see a mutant in your dream
meaning: indicates your fears of things that are different. The dream is trying to teach you to be more open and tolerant of things that you may not be used to.

context: To see mustard growing in your dream
meaning: signifies success and wealth.

context: To dream that you are eating mustard seeds
meaning: indicates regret over your hasty decisions.

context: To dream that you are mute
meaning: indicates that you are afraid to say something for fear of being criticized or judged. There may also be a situation in your waking life that has left you speechless.

context: To dream that you are being mutilated
meaning: indicates that there is a waking situation that you need to be careful about. You may be putting yourself in some sort of danger, either physical or mental. If you are mutilating yourself, then it means that you are seeking attention. You are expressing a desperate cry for help. Or you are trying to disconnect yourself from the unbearable pain you are experiencing in an aspect of your life.

context: To dream that someone or something is mutilated
meaning: indicates that your integrity is put into question.

context: To see or use a muzzle in your dream
meaning: suggests that you need to show better restraint in holding back your anger. Alternatively, the dream indicates that you feel you are unable to fully express yourself.

context: To see myrrh in your dream
meaning: signifies punishment or suffering. You are undergoing a difficult and tumultuous time.

context: To see a myrtle in your dream
meaning: symbolizes happiness, peace, prosperity or domestic bliss.

context: To see the letter "A" in your dream
meaning: represents the beginning of a new stage. You are moving on to something new and grand. Alternatively, the letter "A" invokes feelings of superiority and grandeur. It may indicate the name or initial of a person.

context: To see an aardvark in your dream
meaning: indicates that you are being very secretive and cautious about your business.

context: To see or use an abacus in your dream
meaning: refers to your outdated views. You have an old fashion perspective on certain issues.

context: To see or eat abalone in your dream
meaning: indicates a transitional period in your life. The symbol may also be a play on words to indicate feelings of "loneliness".

context: To dream that you are abandoned
meaning: suggests that it is time to leave behind past feelings and characteristics that are hindering your growth. Let go of your old attitudes. A more direct and literal interpretation of this dream indicates you have a fear of being deserted, abandoned, or even betrayed. It may stem from a recent loss or a fear of losing a loved one. The fear of abandonment may manifest itself into your dream as part of the healing process and dealing with losing a loved one. It may also stem from unresolved feelings or problems from childhood. Alternatively, the dream indicates that you are feeling neglected or that your feelings are being overlooked. Perhaps the dream is a metaphor that you need to approach life with "reckless abandon" and live more freely.

context: To abandon others in your dream
meaning: suggests that you are overwhelmed by the problems and decisions in your life.

context: To see an abbey in your dream
meaning: signifies spirituality, peace of mind and freedom from anxiety. You are in a state of contentment and satisfaction. Help for you is always around the corner.

context: To see an abbey in ruins
meaning: indicates feelings of hopelessness. You have a tendency to not finish what you started.

context: To see an abbot in your dream
meaning: suggests that someone has power over you and are making you do things that you do not necessarily want to do. You are feeling confined or restricted. The dream indicates that you will experience many obstacles and setback before achieving success and prestige.

context: To see abbreviations in your dream may
meaning: represent the initials of someone in your life. The abbreviations could stand for an organization or a common acronym or it may spell out some hidden message or advice. The dreaming mind likes to make use of puns, as well as shorthand messages. For example, "CD" could be a pun on a "seedy" situation. "AA" could stand for Alcoholics Anonymous and thus point to the dangers or your excesses and negative behaviors. "Inc" may represent an "inkling", hunch or suspicious you have about a situation. The initails DM may refer to a direct message or perhaps that you need to check Dream Moqds for your dream anaylsis.

context: To see your abdomen in a dream
meaning: refers to your natural instincts and repressed emotions. There is something in your real life that you "cannot stomach" or have difficulties accepting. You need to get it out of your system. Alternatively, the dream symbol may be strictly physiological and you may just be experiencing constipation or indigestion.

context: To dream that your abdomen is exposed
meaning: represents issues you have with trust and feelings of vulnerability. You are expressing your primal emotions and instincts.

context: To dream that your abdomen is swollen
meaning: indicates that some new project is in the works.

context: To dream of being abducted
meaning: indicates that you are being manipulated by your circumstances or by someone. You lack control of your own life.

context: To witness an abduction in your dream
meaning: signifies feelings of helplessness.

context: To dream that you are abducting someone
meaning: implies that you are holding on to something that you need to let go. You may be forcing your views and opinions on others.

context: To dream that you abhor a person
meaning: represents your waking dislike for that person. You are harboring feelings of resentment or aggression and feel that this person has acted in a less than honorable way.

context: To dream that you are abhorred by others
meaning: suggests that you may be forcing your views and opinions on others. You are rubbing others the wrong way.

context: To dream of some abnormality or of abnormal objects
meaning: indicate that the problems that have been preoccupying your mind will soon be resolved. Note that anything appearing abnormal draws attention to that particular aspect. Something in your life may not be consistent with how you feel things should be.

context: #Ref:home
meaning: #Ref:home

context: #Ref:yeti
meaning: #Ref:yeti

context: To see an Aborigine in your dream
meaning: represents both your untamed, natural self and your pure, innocent side. You need to be more in touch with your intuition and inner forces. It also suggests that you are being overindulgent or overly emotional. You may be harming yourself and jeopardizing your well-being due to your unrestraint.

context: To dream that you have an abortion
meaning: suggests that you are hindering and blocking your own growth. You may be hesitant in pursuing a new direction in your life due to fear, pressure, personal conflict or moral obligation. The dream may also be a reflection of your own real-life abortion and thus serves as a way of healing from the trauma and working towards self-acceptance. Alternatively, this dream may also be a message for you to take care and look after your health.

context: To dream that someone has an abortion
meaning: refers to an aspect of your relationship with this person is not growing or maturing. If you do not know this person, then the dream may be about your own personal views on abortion.

context: To dream that you or someone has an illegal abortion
meaning: indicates that you are desperate to keep things the exact same. If the abortion results in death, then it means that your approach to a problem is all wrong.

context: To see something above you in your dream
meaning: suggests that you need to set your goals higher. Aim high! Alternatively, the dream indicates that you are feeling inferior or inadequate.

context: To see Abraham Lincoln in your dream
meaning: refers to your solid character and leadership ability. Known as "Honest Abe", the dream may also be telling you to be truthful or to come clean about something.

context: To dream of being or going abroad
meaning: indicates unbalance and chaos in your current situation and condition. Consequently, your dream may represent your need for a change in scenery or a desire to escape from a current situation. You need to make some drastic changes in your life. Alternatively, the dream may suggest that you need to expand your horizons or experience a new sense of spirituality.

context: To dream that someone is absent, especially if you expect to find them,
meaning: suggests that you are looking for something that is already lost to you. Alternatively, you may be looking to fill a void in your life. Something is missing from your life.

context: To dream that you have an abscess
meaning: suggests that there is something that you need to express and get out into the open.

context: To dream that you have absconded with something
meaning: indicates your failed accomplishments. You may also be feeling insecure about your achievements. You feel that you are never good enough. Consider the significance or value of what you have absconded.

context: To be absorbed in whatever you are doing
meaning: suggests that you may be too focused on your own thing and risk alienating others around you. The dream may also be a metaphor that you need to integrate and adapt to your various surroundings.

context: To dream that you practice abstinence from drinking, sex or any other sort of sensual temptation
meaning: is a warning against being over confidant. You need to take things more slowly.

context: To dream of having an abundance of a certain item
meaning: indicates that you need to conserve your resources and energies. This dream may be a compensatory dream for something that you are lacking in life. More directly, abundance signifies happiness.

context: To dream you are abusing someone
meaning: suggests that your past actions will come back to haunt you. You may be expressing some regret or remorse over your actions.

context: To dream you are being verbally or physically abused
meaning: suggests that you are feeling victimized in a waking situation. You are being taking advantage of.

context: To see children being abused in your dream
meaning: implies that you are lacking a voice for your own inner child. You feel that a part of your own childhood is lost.

context: To dream of an abyss
meaning: signifies an obstacle that is creating much anxiety for you. You need to work through the difficulty and overcome this obstacle in your life. Perhaps you are afraid of "taking the plunge".

context: To dream that you are falling into an abyss
meaning: symbolizes the depths of your subconscious. You are afraid and/or uncertain as to what you will discover about yourself and about your hidden feelings and fears. The abyss may also represent your primal fears and feelings of "falling into a pit of despair". Perhaps you are in a state of depression or wallowing in your negative feelings. Alternatively, the dream could denote your lack of spirituality.

context: To see an acacia tree in your dream
meaning: symbolizes your attitudes with death and your sense of mortality.

context: To dream of an academy
meaning: signifies new friendships and opportunities.

context: To dream that you at the Academy Awards
meaning: indicates that you need to add some glamour into your life. If you win an Oscar, then it implies that you are looking for some sort of acknowledgment in your waking life.

context: To see an accelerator in your dream
meaning: indicates that you will achieve your goals through your own efforts. The dream may also be telling you to slow down.

context: To dream that the accelerator is jammed or broken
meaning: indicates a loss of control in some aspect of your life. You maybe trying to rush through things.

context: To speak with an accent in your dream
meaning: suggests that you are having difficulties conveying your thoughts. Consider how you feel about the accent. If you feel the accent makes you stand out in a negative way, then it signifies feelings of insecurities. If the accent makes you stand out in a positive way, then it symbolizes an air of confidence.

context: To hear someone speaking with an accent in your dream
meaning: represents something familiar yet different. You are getting the gist of a message, but you still do not completely understand all of it.

context: To dream about acceptance
meaning: indicates issues of self-esteem and measuring up to the expectations of others. There is a waking situation where you are seeking acceptance and wanting to be a part of.

context: To dream of accessorizing yourself
meaning: suggests that you are feeling incomplete. Something is missing in your life.

context: To dream that you are in an accident
meaning: signifies pent-up guilt in which you are subconsciously punishing yourself over. Perhaps you are not proud of something you have done. Alternatively, the accident may symbolize an error or mistake you have made. Accident dreams also represent your fears of being in an actual, physical accident. You may simply be nervous about getting behind the wheel. Or the dream is trying to warn you of some accident.

context: To dream of a car accident
meaning: symbolizes your emotional state. You may be harboring deep anxieties and fears. Are you "driving" yourself too hard? Perhaps you need to slow down before you hit disaster. You need to rethink or re-plan your course of actions and set yourself on a better path. Dreaming that someone is injured in a car accident means that you cannot control the action of others. They have to live with the consequences of their own decisions.

context: To dream that a loved one dies in an accident
meaning: indicates that something within your own Self is no longer functional and is "dead". It is also symbolic of your own relationship with that person. Perhaps you need to let go of this relationship. If you dream that you die from a car accident and actually see the reactions of your loved ones, then it suggests that your reckless activity is affecting those around you. This dream is a wake-up call.

context: To dream that you are an accomplice to a crime
meaning: suggests that someone in your waking life is having a negative influence on you. You may be experiencing feelings of guilt with something that you have done.

context: To dream that you have an accomplice
meaning: implies that others are enabling your negative habits or behavior.

context: To hear the music of an accordion
meaning: signifies some saddening and depressing matter. You need to focus on more joyous moments.

context: To dream that you play the accordion
meaning: denotes intense emotions that are causing physical strain to your body. You are feeling weary. Alternatively, the dream suggests that you need to work hard to achieve your goals.

context: To see or dream that you are an accountant
meaning: represents your objectivity toward some situation. You are taking a step back and looking carefully at the facts.

context: To dream about your bank accounts
meaning: indicates financial worries.

context: To dream that you are being accused of something
meaning: indicates overwhelming feelings of guilt. It may also mean that you are having some doubts about yourself and the choices you are making.

context: To dream that you accuse others
meaning: signifies disagreements and dissension with those around you.

context: To see the ace in the deck of cards
meaning: suggests ambiguity in your life. You need some clarity. In particular, the ace of hearts means that you are involved in some love affair. If you see the ace of spades in your dream, then it means that you are involved in a scandal. If you see the ace of diamonds, then it symbolizes your legacy or reputation. And if you see the ace of clubs, then it indicates that you will be involved in some legal matter.
Alternatively, the dream may be a metaphor that you are an "ace". Or the dream is a pun on "acing" a test.

context: To dream that you have aches
meaning: indicate some hesitation and reluctance in the pursuit of your goals. If you wait too long, then the opportunity may escape.

context: To dream of an achievement
meaning: denotes that you will be greatly satisfied with the outcome of a situation or project. The bigger the achievement, the greater the satisfaction.

context: To see acid in your dream
meaning: represents feelings of hatred, rage, and/or revenge. Your integrity may be compromised or called into question. Alternatively, seeing acid in your dream indicates that you are being manipulated by a situation or by someone. The dream may also be a metaphor to symbolize a negative influence in your life. Something or someone is eating away at you.

context: To dream that you drink acid
meaning: indicates that you are emotionally paralyzed and need to learn how to express yourself.

context: Dreaming of acid rain
meaning: indicates that you have been mislead. You are letting hatred and revenge take over and define you.

context: #Ref:pimples
meaning: #Ref:pimples

context: To see an acorn in your dream
meaning: symbolizes strength and durability. Seemingly small beginnings will have the greatest potential for growth. Don't underestimate your minor goals. Alternatively, the dream means that you are about to enter a new phase in your life.

context: To dream that you are eating acorns or picking them from the ground
meaning: suggests that you will enjoy the benefits of your success after long and hard work.

context: To dream that you are shaking acorns from a tree
meaning: indicates that you have significant influence on others.

context: To see an acquaintance in your dream
meaning: represents aspects of yourself that you are still trying to get to know.

context: To dream that you are disputing with an acquaintance
meaning: represents aspects of yourself that you are rejecting. You are refusing to accept certain things about yourself.

context: To dream that you are acquitted of a crime
meaning: represents a valuable lesson to be learned.

context: To see others acquitted in your dream
meaning: indicates that you need to balance your hard work with fun and pleasure.

context: To see or do acrobats in your dream
meaning: suggest that you need to better balance aspects of your life. It could also mean that fears will prevent you from achieving your goals. Alternatively, acrobatics in your dream may be a metaphor for sexual intercourse.

context: If you are wearing fake fingernails in your dream
meaning: then it suggest that you are reaching out to others, but do not have their best interest in mind. You may be acting in a disingenuous way.

context: To dream that you are acting
meaning: indicates that you are putting up a front and pretending to be someone you are not in some waking situation.

context: To see or dream that you are playing with an action figure
meaning: suggests that you are being manipulated in some way. Or you tend to do what other people expect of you. Consider the significance of the way that the action figure is dressed.

context: To see an actor or actress in your dream
meaning: represents your pursuit for pleasure. Your admiration of a particular celebrity may lead to a desire to have some of their physical or personality traits. Consider also who this actor/actress is and what characteristics you associate with her or him. These may be the same characteristics that you need to acknowledge or incorporate into yourself. The dream may also be a pun on her or his name.

context: To dream that you are an actor
meaning: denotes that your hard work and labor will be well worth it in the end. It also indicates your strong desires to be recognized and acknowledged. Perhaps you are putting too much emphasis on your outward appearances. Alternatively, the dream may be analogous to the role that you are playing in your real life, whether it be the role of a parent, sibling, co-worker, etc. Or perhaps you are putting on an act or a facade.

context: More specifically, if you dream that you are a supporting actor or supporting actress
meaning: implies that you need to be supportive to those around you. It may seem that your presence doesn't matter, but you play an important part to someone's life. To dream that you are an extra in a movie means that you feel unimportant and unnoticed. Sometimes you feel you are blending in with the background.

context: To dream that you are getting acupuncture
meaning: suggests that you are in need of healing. You may need to divert your energies to different pursuits. Alternatively, the dream may be a metaphor for a problem or issue that you need to pinpoint.

context: To see Adam and Eve in your dream,
meaning: suggests that you are ignoring the masculine aspect of yourself (if you are female) or the feminine aspect of yourself (if you are male). Adam and Eve are classic symbols of the animus and anima. Alternatively, the dream indicates an occurrence in your life that will cause you to lose your hopes and chances of success.

context: To dream that you are adamant
meaning: signifies that you will be thwarted in some desire that you held ever so highly in your life.

context: To see an adder in your dream
meaning: symbolizes a sly or cunning person. This person cannot be trusted. It may also represent something or someone who has slipped out of your hands. The dream may also be a pun on something that you need to add to your life.

context: To dream that you are an addict
meaning: indicates that you are no longer in control of a situation. You have surrendered your power and denied responsibility for your actions. The dream is also representative of fear, low self-esteem issues, and insecurities.

context: To dream that you have an addiction or become addicted
meaning: represents an obsessive behavior. A situation or a person may be trying to take over your sense of control. The dream also suggests that you have difficulty relating to the world around you.

context: To dream that you are solving an addition problem
meaning: represents something that is straightforward or obvious. Do not read too much into a problem.

context: To dream that you cannot add correctly
meaning: indicates confusion and chaos. A more directly interpretation suggests that something in your waking life does not add up.

context: To dream of your old address
meaning: suggests that you need to take a look back at the past and learn from it. To dream of a new address indicates the need for change.

context: To dream that you are addressing an envelope
meaning: represents your need to explore more possibilities. Weigh your options carefully before making a final decision. Alternatively, the dream suggests that you have found your direction in life and are ready to pursue your goals.

context: #Ref:goodbyes
meaning: #Ref:goodbyes

context: To see or dream that you are an admiral
meaning: represents your ability to tackle life's issues and problems with confidence and decisiveness. The admiral may also symbolize a father figure or authoritative person.

context: To dream that you are admiring someone
meaning: indicates that you need to incorporate the qualities of that person into your Self.

context: To dream that you are admiring yourself
meaning: suggests that you are in need of approval and affirmation from others. Alternatively, it may mean that you have a large ego or think overly highly of yourself.

context: To see an adobe structure in your dream
meaning: symbolizes protection. It also implies that you are well insulated from life's problems. Perhaps you are being too sheltered and are lacking experience in certain areas of your life. Alternatively, an adobe building represents tradition, hard work and a simple way of life. Maybe you need to incorporate these qualities into your waking life.

context: To dream that you or others are adopting a child
meaning: indicates that you are taking on something new and different. Ask yourself what is missing in your life that would make you happy.

context: To dream that you are adopted
meaning: suggests that you are longing for the child within you.

context: Dreaming of adopting a dog
meaning: symbolizes your desire for a loyal relationship. If you are adopting a cat, then it means that you are embracing a newfound independence.

context: To dream that you seek adulation
meaning: signifies that you will arrogantly step up to undeserved position of honor.

context: To dream that you are offering adulation
meaning: denotes that you are willing to part with something near and dear to you in the hopes of material advancement.

context: If you are a child or teenager and dream that you are an adult,
meaning: then it implies that you need to be more mature about some situation. Perhaps you have some growing up that you need to do. Alternatively, the dream may be reinforcing your sense of responsibility.

context: To dream that you commit adultery or have an affair
meaning: signifies your sexual urges and desires that are longing to be expressed. Alternatively, it indicates self-betrayal of your subconscious. You may find yourself entangled in a situation that is not in your best interest, perhaps even illegal.

context: To dream that your mate, spouse, or significant other is cheating on you
meaning: highlights your insecurities and your fears of being abandoned. You feel that you are being taken for granted. You are lacking attention in the relationship or that he or she is being less affectionate. Alternatively, you feel that you are not measuring up to the expectations of others.

context: To dream that you are advancing in some situation
meaning: signifies your rapid rise to success and honor. Affairs of the heart will also be in your favor.

context: To see others advancing ahead of you
meaning: denotes that others have more important and favorable positions. You need to stop constantly comparing yourself to others.

context: To dream that you are an adventurer
meaning: indicates that you are lacking adventure in your waking life. You need some excitement and variety. Alternatively, the dream suggests that you are too absorbed with your ambition that you do not take the time to acknowledge those who have helped you along the way.

context: To dream that you are confronted by an adversary
meaning: represents a conflict or a fear that you are facing in your waking life. You are in denial or are rejecting an aspect of yourself.

context: To dream that you overcome an adversary
meaning: indicates a resolution to some inner conflict or waking life problem.

context: To dream that you are met with adversity
meaning: represents the obstacles that you are facing in your waking life. You feel that you have failed.

context: To dream that others are in adversity
meaning: signifies your pessimistic outlook in life. You need to learn to see the brighter side of things.

context: To dream that you are looking through advertisements
meaning: represents a message conveyed to you via your subconscious. You need to act on some problem, decision or opportunity. Consider the content of the ads to determine what area of your life needs to be recognized or acknowledged. If someone you know is advertising themselves, then it suggests that this person can help you in your current situation. You may need to learn to ask for help when you need it.

context: To dream that you are putting out an advertisement
meaning: indicates hard work is needed to achieve your goals.

context: To dream that you are receiving advice
meaning: suggests that you need to listen to your instinct and gut.

context: To dream that you are giving advice
meaning: indicates that you have the knowledge and information to help others.

context: To dream that you are an advocate for a cause
meaning: signifies your faithfulness and conviction towards your interest and your loyalty to your friends.

context: To dream that you are doing aerobics
meaning: suggests that you need to get out there and be more active. You need to exercise more.

context: To see an aerosol can in your dream
meaning: indicates that you may be feeling under pressure. You need a release.

context: To dream that you are showing your affections for someone
meaning: represents your satisfaction and happiness with a current relationship. It may also indicate your need to be more affectionate to the ones you love and care about. Alternatively, dreaming about affection may be an indicator that you are lacking affection in your waking life.

context: #Ref:scared
meaning: #Ref:scared

context: To dream of an afterlife
meaning: refers to your desire of escaping from your own reality. You are feeling disconnected from life and society and want to make a fresh start.

context: To dream of the afternoon time
meaning: suggest that it is time to put your energies to good use. Draw and learn from your past experiences and lessons. Alternatively, it symbolizes clarity to a situation.

context: To dream that you have an affliction
meaning: signifies bad news and possible disaster.

context: To dream others afflicted in your dream
meaning: denotes that you will find yourself surrounded by grief and misfortune.

context: To dream that you are affluent
meaning: represents your achievements and the rewards you reap for your hard work. The dream may be a metaphor for your enriching and fulfilling life.

context: To dream that you are affronted
meaning: suggests that someone is working against you and taking advantage of your ignorance or naivet. You may find yourself in a compromising situation.

context: To dream about or that you in Africa
meaning: reflects your desires to return to your roots. You want to find out more about your heritage. If you are traveling to Africa or thinking about visiting Africa, then your dream may indicate your anticipation of such a trip. Or if you have lived in Africa or been there, then the dream reflects your personal feelings and memories about the continent.

context: To see an African American in your dream
meaning: signifies your roots and heritage. You may need to discover the soul within your own self. Alternatively, the dream may mean that you need to be more expressive and creative.

context: To dream that you have an afro
meaning: signifies creative freedom. You need to be more expressive with your ideas.

context: To see a black agate in your dream
meaning: symbolizes wealth, vigor, and courage.

context: To see a red agate in your dream
meaning: represents peace, longevity, and health.

context: To dream of your age
meaning: signifies you anxiety and concern of growing older. It may also represent some regret or failure in your endeavors.

context: To dream that you are older than you really are
meaning: signifies wisdom. Perhaps you need to be more sensible. Negatively, it may mean your unyielding ways and rigid thinking.

context: To dream that you are younger than you really are
meaning: suggests that you need to be more carefree and be young at heart. Live a little!

context: If you are a parent and dream that your child is younger than he or she really is,
meaning: then it means that you are longing for the past. Perhaps you feel that you are no longer important and wish to regress back to a period where you were more needed. Time is passing you by.

context: To dream that you exhibit aggression in your dream
meaning: denotes repressed sexual needs. It is also a reflection of conflict in your waking life.

context: To dream that you are in agony
meaning: suggests that some decision or nagging problem from your waking life has crept into your dream. It will continue to torment you until it is resolved.

context: To dream that you have agoraphobia
meaning: signifies a fear of being exposed or seen. You don't like being the center of attention or being the focus. The dream may symbolize a real life phobia or highlight feelings of anxiety.

context: To dream of an agreement
meaning: indicates resolution to a conflict or problem. Your subconscious is working in accordance with your conscious.

context: To dream that you are shivering with an ague
meaning: forewarns that you will suffer from a physical disorder.

context: To see others affected with ague in your dream
meaning: suggests that others are offended by your indifference or lack of compassion in some situation.

context: To dream that you have AIDS
meaning: indicates that your psychological integrity is being attacked. You feel defenseless, weak and powerless.

context: To dream that your mate has AIDS
meaning: suggests that you are in an unhealthy or destructive relationship. There is something that you are not expressing to each other.

context: To dream that someone else has AIDS
meaning: signifies your need to be more compassionate and sympathetic to others. Alternatively, the dream may be a pun on "aid". Perhaps someone is looking for your help in something.

context: To dream that you are aiming for something
meaning: indicates that you need to direct your energies better. Keep your sight on the main goal. If you are aiming a gun or weapon, then it represents feelings of anger or pent up sexuality.

context: To dream about the air
meaning: symbolizes creativity and intelligence. If the air is foggy or polluted, then it suggests that your thought process or mind is clouded.

context: To feel cold air in your dream
meaning: signifies discordance in your domestic relations and setbacks in your business affairs. You may be in danger of losing touch with reality.

context: To dream that you are breathing hot air
meaning: signifies the influence of evil around you.

context: To dream that you can bend air
meaning: refers to your ability to control and watch what you say. You are careful in how you choose your words.

context: To dream that the air conditioner is not working
meaning: suggests that you are not able to relax and breathe freely. You may be overly worried about a situation.

context: To see or feel the air conditioner in your dream
meaning: represents purification and relief. You have cooled off from some heated argument.

context: To see or use an air gun in your dream
meaning: symbolizes an unperceived threat. You are letting your guard down in some situation where you need to be vigilant. .

context: To smell air freshener in your dream
meaning: suggests that you are enjoying life's little pleasure. The dream may bring about the past or certain memories. If the air freshener is too overpowering, then it indicates that your mind is not clear. You are exhibiting a lack of judgment.

context: To dream that you are in the air force
meaning: suggests that you need to be more spiritually disciplined.

context: To see or play air hockey in your dream
meaning: refers to something that you need to act quickly on or someone else will.

context: To hear or sound an air horn in your dream
meaning: suggests that you are not taking a matter seriously enough. It is time to focus. Alternatively, an air horn is way for your subconscious to get you to pay attention to an important aspect of the dream.

context: To dream that you are caught in an air raid
meaning: indicates that you are feeling overwhelmed by things that are seemingly coming out of the blue. You feel a lack of control in your life.

context: To dream that you are in an air show
meaning: implies that you are showing off your accomplishments to others. You have achieved your goals and want everyone to know it.

context: To see the airbag in a vehicle deploy in your dream
meaning: forewarns that you will run into a major setback if you keep the pace of your current life path. You need to slow down and take your time. Alternatively, the air bag is symbolic of your support system in your time of need.

context: To see an aircraft carrier in your dream
meaning: suggests that you are preparing to confront your emotions. You are addressing feelings that you have been ignoring or suppressing for too long.

context: To see an airdancer in your dream
meaning: represents someone who wants your full attention. Alternatively, dreaming of an airdancer indicates that you are too yielding in a situation. Stand up for yourself.

context: To see an airplane in your dream
meaning: indicates that you will overcome your obstacles and rise to a new level of prominence and status. You may experience a higher consciousness, new-found freedom and greater awareness. Perhaps you need to gain a better perspective or wider view on something. If the airplane is taking off, then it suggests that an idea or plan is about to "take off" and be put into action. It may also represent your need to get away and escape from your daily life. Dreaming that the airplane sits on the runway and never takes off refers to a real life project or idea that has failed to get off the ground. You are having difficulties getting started on a project.

context: To dream that you are flying an airplane
meaning: suggests that you are in complete control of your destination in life. You are confident and self-assured in your decisions and accomplishments.

context: To dream that you transfer planes
meaning: implies an important transitional phase in your life which will take you away from your intended path. These changes will take you to new directions and new heights of status and recognition.

context: To dream that you miss your connection flight
meaning: indicates that you are feeling helpless and trapped by some situation. You feel that you are being held back, either physically or mentally. Alternatively, the dream may also suggest that you are feeling disconnected in some aspect of your life - work, relationship or home life.

context: To dream that a plane crashes
meaning: suggests that you have set overly high and unrealistic goals for yourself. Your goals may be too high and are impossible to realize. You are in danger of having it come crashing down. Alternatively, your lack of confidence, self-defeating attitude and self-doubt toward the goals you have set for yourself is represented by the crashing airplane; you do not believe in your ability to attain those goals. Loss of power and uncertainty in achieving your goals are also signified.

context: To dream that an airplane is hijacked
meaning: signifies disturbing feelings and past emotions in your subconscious mind.

context: Dreaming of airplanes flying in formation
meaning: represents working together toward a common goal.

context: To see an airplane landing in your dream
meaning: signifies completion of a journey or some task. Some issues that were previously out of control have been resolved.

context: To see an airport in your dream
meaning: symbolizes birth (arrivals) and death (departures). If the airport is busy, then it signifies the desire for freedom, high ideals, ambition, and hopes. It is an indication that you are approaching a new departure in your life. Some new idea is taking off or is ready to take off. You may be experiencing a new relationship, new career path or new adventure.

context: To dream of a deserted airport
meaning: indicates that your plans or goals will be changed or delayed. You are having to put some aspect of your life on hold.

context: To dream that you are walking down or through an aisle
meaning: represents your ability to move forward in life with confidence. There is balance in your life. Alternatively, the dream indicates dissension and disagreements. You are stuck in the middle between two diverging viewpoints.

context: To see alabaster in your dream
meaning: represents success in your love life. You have healthy personal relationships.

context: To dream that you break an alabaster figurine
meaning: signifies grief, sorrow, and regrets.

context: To see or dream that you are Aladdin
meaning: represents realization of your goals or dreams.

context: To hear or pull an alarm in your dream
meaning: suggests that you are experiencing a conflict in a relationship or situation which is giving your much anxiety. You may be questioning the decisions you have made. Alternatively, the dream may be a pun on an "alarming" situation which needs your immediate attention. You need to spring into action quickly.

context: To see or hear an alarm clock in your dream
meaning: represents your anxieties and fixation with time. You fear that you do not have enough time to meet your deadlines or accomplish your goals.

context: To see an albatross in your dream
meaning: represents endurance and freedom.

context: To see a dying or dead albatross in your dream
meaning: symbolizes bad luck and harsh, vulnerable times.

context: To see an albino in your dream
meaning: represents purity or eternal life. You need to be more accepting and tolerant.

context: To dream that you are afraid of the albino figure
meaning: suggests that you are irrationally concerned about the well-being of a loved one. It may also mean denial.

context: To see an album in your dream
meaning: indicates that you are surrounded by true friends.

context: To dream that you are looking through a photo album
meaning: suggests that you are unwilling to let go of your memories and the past. You are idealizing about the past.

context: To dream of alchemy
meaning: suggests that you are going through a period of turmoil, inner transformation, and self-renewal. You are striving toward perfection. Although these may be tough and difficult times, it will have a positive outcome.

context: To dream that you are enjoying alcohol in moderation
meaning: denotes contentment and satisfaction in the decisions that you have made. Success is within your grasp. The dream may also be a metaphor for "spirits" and your need for spiritual enrichment.

context: To dream that you are consuming alcohol in excess
meaning: signifies feelings of inadequacy, worries, regrets and fears of being discovered for who you really are. You are using alcohol as a way to escape or as an excuse for something you did. Alternatively, the dream may be reflective of waking issues and problems of alcoholism. Recovering alcoholics often have dreams of drinking which results in feelings of guilt. Such dreams help to reinforce their sobriety.

context: To dream that someone is an alcoholic (and he/she is not one in real life)
meaning: indicates that this person is in desperate need for an outlet to express himself or herself. He or she may be indirectly asking for help.

context: To see an alder tree in your dream
meaning: symbolizes joy and happiness.

context: To see Alfred E. Newman in your dream
meaning: suggests that you are being self-conscious. You are in a situation where you fear being ridiculed or mocked.

context: To see algae in your dream
meaning: indicates that you need to leave your emotions out of some matter.

context: To dream about Alice in Wonderland
meaning: indicates that you have a distorted self image. Alternatively, the dream refers to your desire to escape from the routine and mundaness of your daily life. You are looking for some excitement.

context: To dream that you are an alien
meaning: symbolizes the undiscovered part of yourself. Your manifestation as an alien may be your way of "escaping" from reality. Dreams of this nature also symbolize your outlandish ideas and your wild imagination.

context: To dream that you are being invaded or abducted by aliens
meaning: indicates your fear of your changing surroundings or your fear of losing your home and family. You feel that your space and/or privacy is being invaded.

context: To see aliens in your dream
meaning: signify that you are having difficulties adapting and adjusting to your new surroundings. You are feeling "alienated" and disconnected. You may also be having difficulties with how to handle or deal with a certain situation or person. On a psychological level, seeing aliens represent an encounter with an unfamiliar or neglected aspect of your own self.

context: Dreaming that you are having sex with an alien
meaning: indicates a desire for something new and different in your sex life.

context: To dream that you are paying alimony
meaning: means that you are paying for your past actions and mistakes.

context: #Ref:eyeofprovidence
meaning: #Ref:eyeofprovidence

context: To dream that you have allergies
meaning: signify your sensitively to some situation. You may feel that you are physically or emotionally restrained from doing something.

context: To see an alley in you dream
meaning: suggests that you have limited options. Consider the phrase "something is right up your alley" to mean that something may be perfect for you. Learn to be more open minded. Alternatively, an alley indicates that you are sidetracked from your goals due to your domestic duties and communal responsibilities. You are experiencing a dilemma in your waking life.

context: To dream that you are walking through an alley
meaning: represents a dead-end. You feel that you have missed out on some opportunity in life. Alternatively, the dream denotes that your reputation is in jeopardy. You feel that you are on the outside.

context: To see an alligator in your dream
meaning: symbolizes treachery, deceit, and hidden instincts. It may be a signal for you to take on a new perspective on a situation. It may also represent your ability to move between the physical, material world of waking life and the emotional, repressed world of the subconscious. Alternatively, the alligator represents healing powers and qualities. An alligator also suggests that you are thick-skinned or insensitive.

context: To dream that you are running away from the alligator
meaning: indicates that you are unwilling to confront some painful and disturbing aspect of your subconscious. There is some potentially destructive emotion that you are refusing to acknowledge and owning up to.

context: Dreaming of a baby alligator
meaning: implies that you are too trusting. If you are bitten by an alligator in your dream, then it indicates that you have not learned from your past mistakes.

context: To dream that you are raped by an alligator
meaning: indicates that you feel violated or taken advantage of in some way. The alligator is symbolic of someone who is ruthless, insensitive and treacherous. This person has a strong hold on you despite your efforts to break free from the unhealthy relationship.

context: According to biblical interpretations, an alligator
meaning: suggests that leviathan is king over the children of pride. (Psa 74:14, Job 41:1,Isa 27:1)

context: To dream of getting an allowance
meaning: symbolizes the rewards of your work. It may be a pun on "allowing". You need to be more yielding to others.

context: To see an alloy in your dream
meaning: indicates that you will experience some complications in your professional life.

context: To see an almanac in your dream
meaning: represents the ups and downs of life. You are experiencing fleeting pleasures and unsteady finances.

context: To see or eat almonds in your dream
meaning: represent success and richness.

context: To see an almond tree in your dream
meaning: signifies happiness. Wedded bliss is also in your near future. Alternatively, it symbolizes your resilience and your ability to bounce back from some adversity or hardship.

context: To dream that you are giving alms
meaning: represent your giving nature.

context: To use aloe in your dream
meaning: suggests that you are ready to heal from some emotional wound. You are ready to forgive or forget about someone's betrayal.

context: To dream that you are alone
meaning: indicates feelings of rejection. You may be feeling that no one understand you.

context: To dream that want to be left alone
meaning: suggests that you are not getting enough alone time in your waking life. Perhaps you feel suffocated or smothered by those around you. You just want time alone with your thoughts or ideas.

context: #Ref:letters
meaning: #Ref:letters

context: To see the altar in your dream
meaning: suggests that you are making a great personal sacrifice. You may also be expressing concerns about your spirituality. The dream may also be a pun on your need to "alter" some behavior, attitude or aspect of your life.

context: To see a priest at the altar in your dream
meaning: signifies strife and disharmony in both your work and home. The dream may also point to some guilt that you are suppressing and refusing to acknowledge.

context: To dream that you are kneeing in front of the altar
meaning: represents unfulfilled desires.

context: In particular, seeing a satanic altar in your dream
meaning: indicates that a dark power or energy is at work.

context: To see or dream that you are an altar boy
meaning: symbolizes innocence and purity.

context: To see alum in your dream
meaning: signifies frustrations on plans that you have set for yourself.

context: To dream that you taste alum
meaning: denotes that you have feelings of regret and remorse over the evil you have done onto an innocent person.

context: To see aluminum in your dream
meaning: signifies your ability to retain what is valuable to you. You are happy with what you have. What may seem insignificant to others is important to you.

context: To dream of being an alumni
meaning: represents completion and a sense of pride or accomplishment. If you dream of being an alumni of a school that you did not attend in real life, then it indicates that you are dealing with past regrets. You are wondering how your life would be had you made different choices.

context: To dream that you or someone has Alzheimer's Disease
meaning: refers to your fear of letting go of the past. You are holding on to old memories for fear of forgetting about them. Alternatively, the dream may be an anxiety dream where you are overly worried about forgetting an important date, appointment or event. If someone in your waking life is suffering from Alzheimer's Disease, then the dream may represent the stress and/or sadness of dealing with the disease.

context: To dream that you are an ambassador
meaning: suggests that you need to be more diplomatic in a situation.

context: To see amber in your dream
meaning: symbolizes the sun and positive energy. Amber is said to have natural healing power. Some believe that the amber can heal sore eyes, sprained limbs or arthritis. Thus the amber in your dream could mean you need to be healed in some way.

Alternatively, to see amber in your dream represents resurrection. Something in your past will prove to be extremely important to your future. It could mean a situation or relationship in your waking life that was once lively, is now non-existent. You feel trapped or that your life is too rigid and inflexible. You need to change your outdated way of thinking and old ideas.

context: To dream about an Amber Alert
meaning: means that you need to be more aware of your surroundings. Perhaps you are overlooking some detail. Consider the significance of the numbers or other information that you see in the Amber Alert and how it relates to an aspect of your waking life.

context: To see an ambulance in your dream
meaning: indicates that your careless activities and indiscretion may lead to major problems and complications. This dream may also stem from your own fears of contracting a disease or your deteriorating health. Perhaps, you should cease what you are doing and pay closer attention to some waking situation.

context: To see an ambulance full of wounded passengers
meaning: signifies a fear of letting go your old Self and making space for the new you. You are projecting your emotional wounds and painful experiences onto others. Alternatively, it may also mean that you are hanging around the wrong crowd and are doing yourself more harm than good.

context: To dream that someone is hit by an ambulance
meaning: suggests that some aspect of your psyche is injured and needs immediate care and attention.

context: Dreaming that you are driving an ambulance
meaning: indicates that you are putting the needs of others before your own. Perhaps you are letting others dictate your direction or goals in life.

context: To dream that you have been ambushed
meaning: forewarns of a danger lurking near you. Your situation has taken an unanticipated turn for the worse. You have been prevented from reaching your goals or destination.

context: To dream that you are lying in ambush
meaning: indicates that you will use underhanded means to achieve your goals.

context: If you are from America and dream of America
meaning: then the dream symbolizes independence and freedom to do what you want. If you are from outside of America, then the dream may represent commercialism, riches, or abundance. Your own political views will also strongly influence this imagery.

context: To see an amethyst in your dream
meaning: signifies peace of mind and satisfaction in your professional and personal life. You are content with where you are in your life. It does not take much to make you happy.

context: To dream that you lose an amethyst
meaning: signifies heartbreaks and disappointments in love.

context: To see or dream that you are Amish
meaning: suggests that you need to concentrate on the more important things and basic necessities in life. Alternatively, the dream indicates that you are wishing for a more simplified life.

context: To see or smell ammonia in your dream
meaning: indicates that there is some distressing or offensive matter that you need to confront.

context: To see ammunition in your dream
meaning: suggests that you are utilizing your power to persuade or protect. Alternatively, it may indicates that you are trying to get your way via destructive means.

context: To see an amoeba in your dream
meaning: implies that you need to be more flexible in your situation and adapt to changes.

context: To dream that you are amorous
meaning: symbolizes temptations. Your personal desires and illicit pleasures may land you into trouble. You will find yourself engulfed in scandal.

context: To dream that others are amorous
meaning: signifies that others will try to persuade you into illicit pleasures and abandon your own sense of morality.

context: To see animals amorous in your dream
meaning: represent animalistic desires. Do not give in to temptation as they will be unfulfilling and unsatisfying.

context: To see an Amphisbaena in your dream
meaning: suggests that you are being pulled in two different directions. You are feeling overburdened and do not know whether you are coming or going. Your actions are counterproductive. Perhaps the dream represents some complicated love triangle. Alternatively, the dream signifies your desires for children.

context: To see or be in an amphitheater in your dream
meaning: refers to the spreading of some wisdom or knowledge.

context: To see an amplifier in your dream
meaning: represents your need to be heard. You need to voice your opinion.

context: To dream that your limbs are amputated
meaning: signifies abandoned talents and serious, permanent losses. It indicates your feelings of frustration, powerlessness and helplessness. Sometimes amputation may also represent a situation that you have been ignoring and has finally reached a crisis point. In particular, to dream that your arms are amputated suggests that you lack motivation. Dreaming that your legs are amputated suggests that you are being limited. Something or someone is hindering your progress and where you want to go in life.

context: To see or wear an amulet in your dream
meaning: indicates your need to feel protected. You are gathering your strength together.

context: To see or be in an amusement park in your dream
meaning: indicates that you need to set some time for more relaxation and enjoyment in your life. The rides, booths and elements in the amusement park are an expression of some aspect of yourself or some area in your life. Look up the symbolism of specific rides for more details. Alternatively, the dream indicates that you are too easily distracted lately.

context: To dream that the amusement park is empty or abandoned
meaning: suggests that you need to open yourself to more fun and adventure.

context: To dream that the rides at the amusement park are breaking down
meaning: means that something in your life is not going as expected.

context: To dream that the amusement park is closed
meaning: suggests that you are denying yourself your time for fun and leisure. You need a break.

context: To see an anaconda in your dream
meaning: symbolizes your creativity and potential. This snakes also calls attention to your sexuality and your need to be more in tune with your own sexuality.

context: To dream about anal sex
meaning: represents submission. You may be afraid to yield to the wants and desires of others.

context: To dream that you are an analyst
meaning: suggests that you need to take a closer look at your behavior and actions.

context: To see an analyst in your dream
meaning: indicates that you are not acting appropriately in some situation in your life.

context: To see anarchy in your dream
meaning: suggests that you need to show some restraint when expressing yourself.

context: To dream about your ancestors
meaning: suggest that you are acknowledging your inherited traits and tradition. You may be trying to hold on to the past and preserve it.

context: To see an anchor in your dream
meaning: signifies stability and security. You may be in search for a solid foundation or a firmer ground in your life. Alternatively, an anchor indicates that you are someone who stands firmly on your views and opinions.

context: On the other hand, an anchor
meaning: may be seen as a symbol for something that is holding you back and restraining your freedom. Consider a relationship that may not be working or a career that is going nowhere for you.

context: To dream of an ancient theme
meaning: symbolizes your sense of foundation. You are well-grounded and are able to learn from your past.

context: To see andirons supporting burning logs in your dream
meaning: indicate that you have the support of your friends and family. They are there for you.

context: To see an androgynous person in your dream
meaning: suggests that you are looking to bring together opposing sides and views. Some aspect of your life requires integration.

context: To see or dream that you are an android
meaning: suggests that you have lost your liveliness and sense of spirit. Your life is becoming to monotonous. Alternatively, the dream indicates that you are acting without thinking.

context: To tell or read an anecdote in your dream
meaning: indicates that there is some life lesson or moral that you need to learn or recognize. Alternatively, it refers to your idealistic notions.

context: To see anemones in your dream
meaning: represent distrust and/or death. It is indicative of a transitional phase in your life.

context: To be under anesthesia in your dream
meaning: suggests that you are trying to suppress your emotions instead of confronting them. There may be situation in your life that you are desperately trying to avoid. You are refusing to take responsibility for your actions.

context: To dream that you have an aneurysm
meaning: indicates that you are under some sort of pressure. There is a situation or problem that is causing you a lot of stress. If the aneurysm is in your brain, then it implies that you are under mental stress. If it is near your heart, then it indicates emotional stress.

context: To see angels in your dream
meaning: symbolize goodness, purity, protection, comfort and consolation. Pay careful attention to the message that the angels are trying to convey. These messages serve as a guide toward greater fulfillment and happiness. Alternatively, it signifies an unusual disturbance in your soul. Angels may appear in your dream as a result of your wicked and mean-hearted activities.

context: To dream that you are an angel
meaning: suggests that you are feeling good about something your said or did.

context: In particular, to see three angels in your dream
meaning: symbolize some sort of divinity. It is considered a particularly spiritual and holy dream.

context: To see an angel holding a scroll in your dream
meaning: indicates a highly spiritual dream. Your future and goals are more clearer to you. The message on the scroll is particularly significant.

context: To see an angel of death in your dream
meaning: refers to some abrupt end to a situation, habit or relationship in your waking life. Alternatively, the angel of death represents aspects of yourself that you have rejected or repressed.

context: To dream that you are holding or expressing anger
meaning: symbolizes frustrations and disappointments in your Self. You tend to repress your negative emotions or project your anger onto others. You need to look within yourself.

context: Anger
meaning: Being angry in your dream may have been carried over from your waking life. Dreams function as a safe outlet where you can express your strong and/or negative emotions. You are suppressing your anger and aggression, instead of consciously acknowledging them.

context: Angling
meaning: To dream that you are angling is a good omen of fortune and luck.

context: To see animals in your dream
meaning: represent your own physical characteristic, primitive desires, and sexual nature, depending on the qualities of the particular animal. Animals symbolize the untamed and uncivilized aspects of yourself. Thus, to dream that you are fighting with an animal signifies a hidden part of yourself that you are trying to reject and push back into your subconscious. Refer to the specific animal in your dream. If you dream of two animals fighting, then it points to some sort of sexual tension.

context: Dreaming of animals being abused
meaning: indicates that your own primal desires are being suppressed. You are unable to fully express an important part of who you are. Alternatively, the dream represents your helplessness in a situation.

context: To dream that animals can talk
meaning: represent superior knowledge. Its message is often some form of wisdom. Alternatively, a talking animal denotes your potential to be all that you can be.

context: To dream that you are saving the life of an animal
meaning: suggests that you are successfully acknowledging certain emotions and characteristics represented by the animal. The dream may also stem from feelings of inadequacy or being overwhelmed. If you are setting an animal free, then it indicates an expression and release of your own primal desires.

context: To see lab animals in your dream
meaning: suggest that an aspect of yourself is being repressed. You feel that you are not able to fully express your desires and emotions. Alternatively, it suggests that you need to experiment with your fears, choices, and beliefs. Try not to limit yourself.

context: Animal
meaning: A dream about a baby animal is often symbolic of your own child.

context: To dream that you are at an animal shelter
meaning: indicates that you are feeling shut out of some situation or relationship. It may also represent feelings of being unwanted or unloved.

context: To dream that you are watching animation
meaning: suggests that you can find the humor and comedy in most situations. You are taking things light-heartedly.

context: To dream that you are watching anime
meaning: represents your carefree attitude.

context: To dream that you are an anime character
meaning: suggests that you need to be more expressive. You need to convey your emotions more clearly.

context: To dream that there is animosity towards you
meaning: suggests that you need to reevaluate a situation and rethink your issues of morality.

context: To see an ankh in your dream
meaning: symbolizes empowerment, infinite knowledge, sexual connection or eternity.

context: To dream about your ankles
meaning: indicates that you are seeking support and direction in your life. Ask yourself where you want to be headed.

context: To sprain your ankle in your dream
meaning: suggests that you are experiencing some obstacles or difficulties in your progress.

context: To dream that your ankles are swollen
meaning: indicates that you are headed down the wrong path. Alternatively, the dream is telling you to get off your feet and relax. You are pushing yourself too hard.

context: To see or dream that you are wearing an ankle monitor
meaning: indicates that you are feeling scrutinized about every step or decision your make. You are afraid of making a wrong move.

context: To see or wear an anklet in your dream
meaning: refers to the way that your life going and the decisions you made to get to where you are. It also signifies passion and lust.

context: To dream about your anniversary
meaning: represents acceptance or appreciation of some aspect of yourself. Consider the type of anniversary. If it is a wedding anniversary, then it symbolizes a celebration of love. You need to accept love into your life. If it is an anniversary of a death or some solemn occasion, then it suggests a new start. The dream may simply mean a reminder of some important date.

context: To hear an announcer in your dream
meaning: indicates that you are being watched. Someone is watching your moves or are taking interest in your actions. Alternatively, hearing an announcer in your dream represents a voice from your subconscious.

context: If you dream that you hear an announcer at a sporting event,
meaning: then it parallels the actions that you need to take in some area of your waking life.

context: To dream that you are an announcer
meaning: means that you are busy observing things going around you instead of partaking in the action.

context: To feel annoyed in your dream
meaning: represents annoyances that you are feeling in your waking life. Something in your mind is bothering you and you need to express them.

context: To dream that you are getting an annulment
meaning: suggests that you are in denial about something.

context: To dream that you have anorexia
meaning: represents your lack of self-acceptance and self-esteem. You need to learn to love yourself and accept who you are instead of punishing yourself. The dream symbolizes your quest for perfection.

context: To see an answering machine in your dream
meaning: suggests that you are not listening to a message that someone around you is trying to convey. Perhaps you are experiencing difficulties and frustration in understanding some idea or viewpoint.

context: To dream that you are in Antarctica
meaning: represents the challenges and hardships in your waking life and your ability to endure it all.

context: To dream that you live in Antarctica
meaning: symbolizes your tenacity and drive, even though the odds may be against you.

context: To see an anteater in your dream
meaning: indicates that you need to proceed with caution in some endeavor.

context: To see an antelope in your dream
meaning: suggests that your high ambitions will only be achieved through a great expenditure of energy. You will experience much success as a result of your dedication. Alternatively, the dream may be telling you to flee or retreat from some situation.

context: To see an antelope collapse in your dream
meaning: means that you are at fault for a broken-up love affair.

context: To see an antenna in your dream
meaning: represents your communication with your surroundings. Consider the condition of the antenna to determine your ability to transmit your ideas and convey your thoughts to others.

context: To see an anthill in your dream
meaning: suggests that you are trying to avoid doing any hard work. You are feeling lazy.

context: To dream that you are taking antibiotics
meaning: suggests that there is some negativity that you are trying to protect yourself against.

context: To dream that you need an antidote
meaning: suggests that you are seeking some sort of balance in your life. You may be looking to right a wrong that you have done in the past.

context: To see or use antifreeze in your dream
meaning: suggests that you are being emotionally cold and perhaps need to warm up to others more.

context: To dream that you are using an antiseptic
meaning: symbolizes healing and cleansing. You need to stay away from negative thoughts and think more positively.

context: To dream that you are feeling or being antisocial
meaning: suggests that you are not getting enough alone time in your waking life. Perhaps you feel suffocated or smothered by those around you. You just want time alone with your thoughts or ideas. Alternatively, antisocial sentiments points to feelings of being misunderstand.

context: Antlers
meaning: To see antlers in your dream are representative of masculine sexuality, male aggression and assertiveness. It may also be symbolic of a trophy or prize.

context: To see ants in your dream
meaning: signify your general dissatisfaction in your daily life. You are feeling neglected and insignificant. Or petty things will annoy you throughout the following day. The dream may also be a metaphor on feeling antsy or restless. It may also be a pun on your "aunt".

context: Ants also
meaning: symbolize hard work, diligence, cooperation and industry. Increase business activities are expected. On a less positive note, ants symbolize social conformity and mass action. In this regard, you may feel that your life is too structured and orderly.

context: According to the biblical interpretations, ants
meaning: symbolize diligence concerning the things of God. Despite its small size, the ant lays up substance during times of plenty. (Prov 30:25)

context: To see Anubis in your dream
meaning: indicates you are in search of clarity. You need some spiritual guidance. Alternatively, it suggests that death is near.

context: To see your anus in your dream
meaning: signifies negative emotions that you may be holding in and repressing. It represents feelings of guilt, shame, and self-worth. Alternatively, the anus is associated with either your generosity or stinginess. Consider also you or someone in your life who may be anal retentive and perhaps need to loosen up a bit.

context: To see an anvil in your dream
meaning: signifies that you hold the power and key to your own success, although you will surely have to go through some struggle and difficulty to achieve your success.

context: To see a broken anvil in your dream
meaning: denotes that you have let promising opportunities pass you by forever.

context: To experience anxiety in your dream
meaning: is a reflection of what you may be feeling during your waking life. You may have repressed thoughts, unexpressed emotions, resentment, or hostility that are triggering your anxiety dream. This dream also suggests that you are taking on too many responsibilities.

context: To dream about an apartment
meaning: refers to your financial or emotional state. To dream of a large and lavish apartment means that you are headed in the right direction in life. Things will improve for you. To dream of a rundown or messy apartment indicates some financial or emotional turmoil in your life.

context: To see an ape in your dream
meaning: indicates deception, mischievous, and falsehood. Alternatively, it may refer that you or someone have gone "ape". You need to calm down. The ape may also symbolize your wild inner nature, particularly your sexual nature.

context: To dream of the apocalypse
meaning: signifies an emotional and dramatic change taken place within yourself. The dream may also indicate the end of one kind of lifestyle and the beginning of another.

context: To see Apollo in your dream
meaning: represents growth. As the sun god, he also signifies enlightenment and insight.

context: To dream that you are apologizing to someone
meaning: refers to your desire for harmony and truth in your waking life. Perhaps you are feeling guilty about something. Or the dream is a way for your subconscious to alert you to some wrongdoing that you are responsible for. Alternatively, an apology symbolizes forgiveness. You need to let go of some grudge.

context: To dream that someone is apologizing to you
meaning: implies that you feel mistreated or wronged. Consider the significance of who is apologizing to you. Perhaps you feel you have betrayed an aspect of your own character.

context: #Ref:clothing
meaning: #Ref:clothing

context: To see an apparition in your dream
meaning: symbolizes your spirit for life. It may also be a message from your subconscious. Alternatively, the dream indicates that someone in your life in not really there for you. Although they are physically present, they are not mentally or emotionally there for you.

context: To dream that things appear out of no where
meaning: suggests that you need to utilize your intellect in a more creative and productive way. You need to think clearly and logically. Consider the symbolism of the objects that appear in your dreams for better understanding of your mind and its intellectual power.

context: To dream about your appearance
meaning: indicates concerns over how others perceive you. If you appear disheveled in your dream, then it implies low self-esteem issues. If you have a good appearance, then it relates to your positive attitude and self confidence.

context: To dream about your appendix
meaning: points to a growing issue that you have been overlooking and requires your immediate attention.

context: Dreaming that you have appendicitis
meaning: means that you are keeping too many feelings bottled up.

context: If you dream that you are having your appendix removed,
meaning: then it indicates that you are confronting some internal hurt that you have been suppressing.

context: To dream of your appetite
meaning: suggests that there is an area if your life that remains unfulfilled. If you feel hungry or thirsty, then it symbolizes lust and sexual desire.

context: To hear applause in your dream
meaning: indicates that you are seeking acclaim and recognition. You need to acknowledge yourself in some area or situation in your life.

context: To dream that you are applauding another
meaning: suggests that you need show more appreciation and praise. Try to be a motivator.

context: To see an apple tree in your dream
meaning: symbolizes grandeur and magnificence. You are feeling larger than life.

context: To see apples growing in a tree in your dream
meaning: symbolize knowledge, wisdom and great prosperity. Rewards are on the horizon for you. Consider also the common phrase, "an apple a day keeps the doctor away" which may imply that you need to take better care of your health. Perhaps you need to go to the doctor. Or the dream may also be a metaphor for a product from Apple.

context: To dream that you are eating an apple
meaning: denotes harmony, pleasure, and fertility. Alternatively, eating an apple in you dream symbolizes your sexual appetite, lustful desires, and sexual awareness.

context: To see green apples
meaning: represent developing love or love that has yet to blossom.

context: To see rotten or eaten apples in your dream,
meaning: indicates that whatever you are striving and aiming for may not be fulfilling, and even harmful to you. It may also represent neglect and carelessness.

context: If you dream that you are picking apples,
