meaning: then it implies that your hard work and dedication will pay off.

context: To make applesauce in your dream
meaning: indicates that you are finding more acceptable ways of expressing your sexual desires.

context: Dreaming of eating applesauce
meaning: reflects your simple tastes.

context: To fix an appliance in your dream
meaning: represents your need to work on your relationship and prevent it from falling apart. Consider the significance of the appliance for clues on specific area of the relationship.

context: To dream that you are filling out an application
meaning: indicates that you are lacking something in your life. Consider the significance of what the application is for and how it relates to your waking life. Alternatively, the dream may be a pun that you need to "apply" yourself. You need to put forth some effort in order to excel or succeed.

context: To dream that you are going to an appointment
meaning: suggests that you need to be more goal-oriented. If you dream that you miss an appointment, then it indicates that you are not paying enough attention to some minor details and little things in life.

context: To dream that you are an apprentice
meaning: suggests that you will have to prove yourself in order to gain acceptance from your colleagues.

context: To dream that you are approaching something or someone
meaning: signifies a careful and well-thought out plan. The dream is telling you that it is time to move forward.

context: To dream that you are being approached
meaning: means that you tend to wait for things to happen instead of making things happen. Be more proactive. Consider the significance of what or who is approaching you.

context: To dream that you are looking for approval from someone
meaning: indicates that you have some dependency issues. You need to stop pleasing others and start thinking about what is best for you.

context: To see the word "approved" in your dream
meaning: indicates that you are making the right choice or decision in life. You are on the right track.

context: To dream that you approve something
meaning: represents your sense of power.

context: To see apricots in your dream
meaning: indicate that something is not what it seems. Perhaps you are in denial about something.

context: To dream that you are eating an apricot
meaning: forewarns of approaching misfortune. If others are eating apricots, then it suggest that you will be surrounded by unpleasantness.

context: To dream of the month of April
meaning: denotes pleasure and profit are in store for you. In particular, to dream about April Fool's day indicates that you are acting like a fool or being foolish.

context: To see an apron in your dream
meaning: suggests that you or someone is making a commitment to work on some familial task. You are trying to nurture some project. Alternatively, an apron symbolizes protection and secrecy.

context: To wear an apron in your dream
meaning: indicates that you are in a submissive position. You are letting others tell you what to do.

context: To see aquamarine in your dream
meaning: symbolizes youth, vitality, creativity, and hope. The dream may be telling you that you need to open the line of communication with someone. It may also share some significance with the symbol for water.

context: To see an aquarium in your dream
meaning: signifies that you have acknowledged your emotions but have not yet confronted them. Thus, it may refer to your subconscious thoughts or repressed sexual desires. Also, you may feel that your life is going nowhere or that you feel it is going in circles. Alternatively, the aquarium may indicate that you need to calm down and set some time for yourself to relax and unwind.

context: To dream that someone is an Aquarius
meaning: represents new ideas, individuality and innovation. You are looking ahead and preparing yourself for the future. It also refers to an aspect of yourself that wants everyone within a group to be happy and satisfied.

context: To see an aqueduct in your dream
meaning: symbolizes your spiritual path.

context: To dream that you are an arbiter
meaning: refers to your control and power over some matter. You feel that you are above the rules.

context: To see or work with an arbiter in your dream
meaning: implies that you are feeling powerless. Alternatively, the dream indicates that you are looking for a resolution to some conflict or problem in your life. The arbiter may represent a spiritual message.

context: To see or draw an arc in your dream
meaning: implies that you are experiencing some setbacks in your plans or goals.

context: To see or dream that you are at an arcade
meaning: suggests that you need to look back to a previous event or experience that brought you much joy and amusement. You want to go back to the good 'ole days. The dream arcade also serves as a temporary escape from reality. You are trying to numb and block out your problems. Alternatively, the dream indicates that you are manipulating others or that you feel manipulated.

context: To see an arch in your dream
meaning: represents your support system.

context: To dream that you are passing under an arch
meaning: signifies new opportunities. You are headed toward a different direction or phase in your life.

context: To dream about archaeology
meaning: indicates your discovery and acknowledgement of your subconscious.

context: To dream that you are an archaeologist
meaning: suggests that you need to learn from past experiences or that you need to look to the past to find answers to present issues.

context: To see an archbishop in your dream
meaning: suggests that someone has power over you and are making you do things that you do not necessarily want to do. Alternatively, you are feeling confined or restricted. You will experience many obstacles and setbacks before achieving success and prestige.

context: To see archery in your dream
meaning: suggests that you are setting your goals and planning your direction in life. It signifies attainment and fulfillment of your goals.

context: To see an architect in your dream
meaning: indicates that your creativity is being put to work. You are taking on a new project which will require such creativity.

context: To dream that you are an architect
meaning: suggests your need for visual stimulation.

context: #Ref:building
meaning: #Ref:building

context: To dream that you are in the Arctic
meaning: symbolizes your emotional state. You may be feeling cold and rigid. Alternatively, it suggests that you are feeling isolated and lonely.

context: To see or dream that you are in an arena
meaning: indicates that you need to be in an environment where you can freely express yourself. You need a stage or platform for your self-expression. Alternatively, the dream may indicate that there is some issue or problem that needs to be brought into the open.

context: To dream that you are arguing
meaning: suggests that you are trying to resolve some internal conflict or some unsettled issue in your waking life. Consider the symbolism of whom you are arguing with and what you are arguing about. How does he or she reflect some person or some aspect of yourself in your waking life?

context: To hear someone arguing
meaning: represents issues that are not being openly discussed or acknowledged. You feel overlooked and that your ideas are unimportant insignificant. Sometimes if you hear family members arguing in real life, it can be incorporated into your own dream.

context: To see argyle in your dream
meaning: refers to your methodical thinking and analytical mind. Perhaps you are overly analytical. Alternatively, argyle indicates monotony. Your life is becoming too routine and repetitious.

context: To dream that someone is an Aries
meaning: suggests new beginnings and growth. It is representative of your leadership, your courage, your passion and your enthusiasm. As represented by the ram, the dream may be telling you that you need to approach an issue or emotion head on. Alternatively, the dream may indicate some mental problem.

context: To dream about arithmetic
meaning: indicates that you are evaluating a situation in your waking life where you need to be more rational in your thinking. Try not to act on your emotions

context: To dream that you are unable to solve an arithmetic problem or equation,
meaning: parallels a waking problem where you may be confused about. The dream may offer a hint toward a new approach to the waking problem. Something does not add up in your life.

context: To see an ark in your dream
meaning: represents rebirth preservation and protection of something valuable. It is symbolic of wholeness.

context: To see or find the Ark of the Covenant
meaning: refers to the strength of your faith and spirituality.

context: To see your arms as the emphasis in your dream
meaning: indicate your nurturance side and your ability to reach out and care for people. Alternatively, it may represent the struggles and challenges in your life. Consider the phrase of "arming yourself" which implies that you need to protect yourself, be more aggressive and take a firmer stance on things or the pun "up in arms", representing anger and your readiness to argue.

context: To dream that your arm has been injured
meaning: signifies your inability to care for yourself or your helplessness in reaching out to others. You may have been feeling limited and restricted in terms of your freedom or activities. The right arm signifies your outgoing nature and is associated with masculine energy, while your left arm signifies your supportive or nurturing nature and is associated with feminine qualities. Losing either arm may suggest that you are failing to recognize its respective characteristics.

context: To dream that you rip someone else's arms out
meaning: indicates that you are extremely upset with something that this person has done, but you have not been able to fully express your anger. Because you tend to keep your emotions inside, it is finding expression in your dreams in a violent way.

context: Dreaming that someone has more than two arms
meaning: symbolizes acceptance, receptiveness or being open minded.

context: To dream that you are arm wrestling
meaning: implies that there is a waking situation that requires you to be more hands on.

context: To see an armadillo in your dream
meaning: represents your need to establish certain boundaries. You may be putting up walls between you and those who want to know you better. Alternatively, it indicates codependency. You need to be more assertive and not let others step all over you.

context: To dream about Armageddon
meaning: suggests that you are feeling hopeless and out of control. The dream may be triggered from the deep emotional stress that you are experiencing in your waking life.

context: To see or sit in an armchair in your dream
meaning: indicates that you are completely secure about your status and position in your waking life. You have established yourself and deserve respect.

context: To dream that you are wearing an armor
meaning: symbolizes your defense mechanisms. You have developed a way of shielding yourself from things that may hurt you. Alternatively, it means that you are feeling invincible and superior.

context: To see armor in your dream
meaning: indicates insecurity. You are worried about your well being.

context: To see or drive an armored car in your dream
meaning: suggests that you are feeling insecure about the progress you have made so far in life. Perhaps you feel that you are not measuring up to others. You are building a protective barrier or emotional wall around yourself. Alternatively, the dream means that you need to be careful of your spending and that you need to protect your finances.

context: To see an armory in your dream
meaning: indicates that you are feeling defensive or protective about something. Alternatively, dreaming of an armory symbolizes your energy reserve. There is still a lot of fighting power in you; don't give up.

context: To see/notice your or someone else's armpit in your dream
meaning: represents your social connections and your relationships to others. It is the characteristics and personality that you chose to display to the public. Alternatively, the dream may refer to something or some place that is smelly.

context: To smell your armpit in your dream
meaning: indicates that you are making some character adjustments in order to smooth over a situation or relationship. Alternatively, it suggests that you are looking for acceptance.

context: To see the army in your dream
meaning: symbolizes an overpowering force working against you. You may feel outnumbered or pressured and are unable to deal with this situation.

context: To dream that you join the army
meaning: suggests your feelings of superiority. You feel that no one is any match for you.

context: To smell certain aromas in your dream
meaning: represents past experiences and feelings that you associate with that particular aroma. Something in your waking life may be triggering this past experience. In particular, if the aroma is sweet, then it symbolizes pleasure and joy.

context: To dream that you are in an arranged marriage
meaning: suggests that you are feeling forced to do something you do not want to do. You are reluctantly moving into a new stage in your life. You feel that you have no voice or no choice in a situation. Consider how a waking situation may be making you feel voiceless.

context: To dream that you are being arrested
meaning: indicates issues of control and restraint. Some aspect of your Self may have been prevented from fully developing. Alternatively, it suggests feelings of guilt.

context: To see an arrow in your dream
meaning: represents the targets you are reaching for and the goals you are setting for yourself. If you are hit by an arrow, then it refers to a release or exposure of some tension and pressure. Consider the body part that the arrow hits.

context: To see an old or broken arrow
meaning: symbolizes disappointments and severed relationships. Alternatively, it may indicate that you have changed your mind about some decision.

context: To see a two-headed arrow in your dream
meaning: signifies opposing ideas and viewpoints. You need to consider both sides.

context: In the Freudian school of thought an arrow
meaning: symbolizes the penis and its ability to penetrate.

context: To see an arrowhead in your dream
meaning: symbolizes your determination, direction and goal. You are planning a path toward success.

context: To see a broken arrowhead in your dream
meaning: represents failure in moving toward your goals.

context: To dream that you find arrowheads
meaning: refer to your abandoned goals. They symbolize your ideas that never took off or came to fruition.

context: To dream about an arson
meaning: represents unexpressed rage that has the potential to become destructive. It is best to express your anger instead of keeping it bottled up inside.

context: To dream that you are in an art class
meaning: means that you need to learn to express yourself in a more creative way. Perhaps you have been suppressing your creative energy and need to let it out.

context: To dream that you are in an art gallery
meaning: represents your past experiences. Something in your past is having an impact in your current situation. Alternatively, the dream may be telling you that you need to capture some moment and preserve it.

context: To see art supplies in your dream
meaning: suggest that you are looking for an outlet to express your creativity. It is also a symbol of possibilities and of your imagination.

context: To see your arteries in your dream
meaning: symbolize how well you carry yourself and your ability to reach out to others. If you dream that your arteries are clogged, then it indicates that some aspect of your personality is hindering your progress or expression.

context: To dream that your artery is severed
meaning: suggests that you still have a lot to learn in life.

context: To dream that you have arthritis
meaning: indicates that you are having difficulties achieving your goals. You are feeling helpless to do anything or are lacking motivation and/or desire to move forward with your plans. Alternatively, it signifies your rigid attitudes.

context: To see or eat an artichoke in your dream
meaning: suggests that you need to get to the heart of some matter. It is also representative of your potential and creativity. Perhaps you are holding back in how you want to express yourself.

context: To see or find an artifact in your dream
meaning: symbolizes an aspect of your former self that you still have not completely let go. Although you may grow and evolve, you never forget where you came from. The artifact may also refer to a prior relationship that you still cherish and look back fondly on.

context: To dream that you are an artist painting a picture
meaning: signifies the creative and intuitive side of your character. The picture that you are painting in your dream may symbolize the way that you are visualizing your current situation in your waking life.

context: To dream that you are buying artwork
meaning: suggests that you are willing to work hard and follow directions. However, you lack leadership abilities.

context: To dream that you are selling artwork
meaning: represents your ability to express yourself and your beliefs.

context: To dream that you have been exposed to asbestos
meaning: refers to some pent up anger that is on the verge of erupting. You have been holding back some of your true feelings for too long. Alternatively, dreaming of asbestos symbolizes a hidden threat. Someone may be trying to keep you from learning the truth.

context: Dreaming of removing asbestos
meaning: indicates regret of something you have done in the past.

context: To see something ascend in your dream
meaning: indicates that you need to have a better or broader outlook on life. It is also symbolic of your lofty aspirations. Or the dream may be a metaphor of your ability to rise above any situation.

context: To see an ash tree in your dream
meaning: represents stability, protection, unity and solidarity. The dream could be telling you that someone in your walking life is offering you protection and stability. The ash tree may also be a pun on "ashes" and of issues related to the past.

context: To see ashes in your dream
meaning: signify disappointments, regrets, bitter changes and disruptions. Ashes also represent a failed relationship or a failed business endeavor. You feel that the good times are over and nothing of value is left in your life. Alternatively, ashes indicates that you are dwelling too much on the past. You need to learn to let go.

context: In particular, to see or clean ashes in a fireplace or stove
meaning: indicates that you are unsatisfied with aspects of your life. You may be in a rut and feel trapped by your daily routine.

context: To see or dream that you are in an ashram
meaning: refers to your need for spiritual renewal and healing. You need to take a break from life's demands so you can replenish your energy.

context: To see or use an ashtray in your dream
meaning: suggests that you are trying to rid yourself of former feelings/memories and your old ways. It symbolizes relationships that have been extinguished and no longer intact. Alternatively, it may be related to feelings of anxieties or connected to your smoking habit, especially if you are trying to quit.

context: To dream that you are in Asia
meaning: suggests that you need to adjust to some situation. If you are traveling to Asia or thinking about visiting Asia, then your dream may indicate your anticipation of such a trip.

context: To see an Asian person in your dream
meaning: represents an aspect of your own self that is unknown to you. Additionally, to see an elderly Asian person represents tradition, wisdom and knowledge.

context: To dream that you are asking someone out on a date
meaning: reflects your anxieties about really asking this person out. The dream serves as a "rehearsal" to help you with your approach. Dreaming of asking someone out may be your unconscious pushing you to go ahead and ask her or him out.

context: To see an asp in your dream
meaning: symbolizes misfortune, loss of honor and respect, and hostility amongst friends and loved ones.

context: To see asparagus in your dream
meaning: symbolizes prosperity.

context: To eat asparagus in your dream
meaning: indicates that your actions will result in an unpleasant outcome.

context: To see an aspen in your dream
meaning: indicates loneliness.

context: #Ref:concrete
meaning: #Ref:concrete

context: To dream that you are being asphyxiated
meaning: implies that you are being smothered or suffocated by a situation or relationship. In particular, if you are in a room or space with no air, then it means that you are feeling trapped by this situation or relationship.

context: To see an ass in your dream
meaning: signifies a lack of understanding. It also suggests that you will come upon many annoyances. The dream may be a metaphor for someone who is being an ass.

context: To see an ass carrying burdens in your dream
meaning: signifies that after much patience and hard work, you will succeed in your professional and personal life.

context: To dream that you have been assassinated
meaning: represents a hopeless situation that needs your immediate attention and action.

context: To dream that you are a witness to an assassination
meaning: indicates that you need to pay more attention to some small detail. Do not overlook the seemingly insignificant things in life. In particular, to dream that an important political figure is assassinated on your watch implies that you are lacking support in your waking life. You feel you are alone in your views and decisions.

context: To dream that you are an assassin
meaning: implies that you are trying to kill an aspect of yourself. Perhaps you are trying to put an end to a habit or relationship. Consider the characteristics of the person you are trying to assassinate and how these qualities relate to you.

context: To dream that you have been assaulted
meaning: refers to a waking situation where you feel vulnerable or helpless. Something in your life is out of your control. In particular, if you dream of being sexually assaulted, then it refers to a situation where you feel violated or victimized. If you have been assaulted in real life, then such dreams may also be a flashback to the actual assault.

context: To dream that you are at an assembly
meaning: suggests that you are learning to accept and integrate the various aspects of yourself. The dream may also be telling you that you need to schedule a meeting. There is something that needs to be discussed.

context: To dream that you are giving assistance to someone
meaning: suggests that you are being called on for support, either emotional support or physical support.

context: To dream that you are being assisted
meaning: denotes your helplessness in a situation.

context: To see an asteroid in your dream
meaning: represents a spiritual message from above. You are about to be enlightened with some knowledge. Alternatively, it signifies a brainstorming of ideas and thoughts. If the asteroid hits the earth, then it indicates that your idealistic notions are deteriorating or being shattered apart.

context: To see asters in your dream
meaning: symbolize your hopes, wishes, and your dreams.

context: If you do not have asthma in your waking life and dream that you have asthma,
meaning: then it refers to insecurity and emotional instability. There is a lot of stress and tension around you. Alternatively, the dream suggests that you need to take a long deep breath in between your problems. If you have asthma, then the dream may be concerns and fears over your waking condition.

context: To dream of astral projection
meaning: suggests that you are looking at things from a whole new perspective. You may be feeling liberated and free. Alternatively, it indicates that you are physically or emotionally disconnected from those around you.

context: To dream about astrology
meaning: suggests that you are concerned about your future. You are looking for some reassurance. Your dream astrological forecast may offer a significant message which should be analyzed closely as it relates to your waking life.

context: To see or dream that you are an astronaut
meaning: indicates that you are expanding your awareness and consciousness. You are utilizing the information you have and making the best of it. Alternatively, the astronaut symbolizes your ambition. You are reaching for the stars. Or it may mean that you are experiencing some communication issues.

context: To see or dream that you are an astronomer
meaning: indicates that you will achieve your goals slowly but surely. You are methodical and careful in your approach to life's obstacles and problems.

context: To see an aswang in your dream
meaning: indicates that you are feeling vulnerable and/or untrusting of others. You are unsure of who are your enemies and friends.

context: To dream that you are an aswang
meaning: implies that you are utilizing deception and underhanded means to get what you want. You are taking advantage of the innocent and the vulnerable.

context: To dream that you are at an asylum
meaning: suggests that you are feeling tremendous mental strain and are trying to reach out for help. You are acknowledging your need for help.

context: To dream that you are an athlete
meaning: suggests that you have pushed yourself to the limits. You have achieved something which you thought you could not do. Just be careful not to overextend yourself.

context: To see a famous athlete in your dream
meaning: refers to a larger than life attitude. Consider the significance of the sport that the athlete is famous for. Famous athletes are also seen as modern day hero archetypes who symbolize champion, courage, and self-sacrifice.

context: To see or dream that you are on an athletic field
meaning: represents the challenges that you are facing in your waking life. It also refers to your competitive nature.

context: To dream that you are looking at an atlas
meaning: indicates your attention to details. You need to plan out your path before moving forward.

context: To see or use an ATM Machine in your dream
meaning: represents your desires for financial security. The dream may be trying to offer reassurance; your fears of financial instability are unfounded. If you are withdrawing money from the ATM Machine, then it suggests that you are expending too much energy on fruitless endeavors and are in danger of depleting your inner resources. If you are depositing money into the ATM Machine, then it symbolizes the energies that you are investing into a project.

context: To dream that the ATM Machine gives you more money that you were due
meaning: refers to your inflated ego. You have a sense of entitlement to certain things.

context: Dreaming that the ATM Machine is spitting out something else instead of money
meaning: highlights your financial concerns. You are spending money on something that could be used towards something more worthwhile. The dream could also be analogous to spending time on something or someone not worthwhile.

context: To see an atom in your dream
meaning: symbolizes unlimited potential. Do not underestimate yourself or others. Alternatively, the dream may be a pun on someone whose name is Adam.

context: #Ref:nuclearbomb
meaning: #Ref:nuclearbomb

context: To dream that you attack someone
meaning: represents pent-up frustration and anger. You feel that you have been wronged. Your dream serves as an easy and safe way to express your anger.

context: To dream that you are being attacked by someone
meaning: indicates your character is being questioned. You feel the need to defend yourself. You are feeling stressed, vulnerable and helpless. You may also be facing difficult changes in your waking life. Dreaming of an attack provides a way for you to confront these situations that you may be avoiding in real life.

context: To dream that you are being attacked by an animal
meaning: is a warning to be careful with those around you. Take notice of who you know in your waking life that shares and exhibits the same qualities of the animal that attacked you in your dream.

context: To dream that you kill an attacking animal
meaning: suggests that you are going against your instincts or gut feeling.

context: To see an attic in your dream
meaning: represents hidden memories or repressed thoughts that are being revealed. It also symbolizes your mind, spirituality, and your connection to the higher Self. Alternatively, it signifies difficulties in your life that may hinder you from attaining your goals and aspirations. However, after a long period of struggle, you will overcome these difficulties.

context: To see a cluttered attic in your dream
meaning: is a sign to organize your mind and thoughts. Perhaps, you need to rid yourself of the past and let go of the past emotions that are holding you back.

context: To see an attorney in your dream
meaning: suggests that you are seeking guidance and advice.

context: To see or ride an ATV in your dream
meaning: indicates your desire to get off the beaten path. You want create your own path and do things your way. Alternatively, the dream suggests that you need to find time for some solitude in your life.

context: To dream that you are at an auction
meaning: indicates that you may be undervaluing or overvaluing something or some relationship. It may also mean that you have learned from your past experiences and are ready to move on.

context: To dream that someone outbid you in an auction
meaning: suggests that you are being denied something that you have earned.

context: To dream that no one is bidding at an auction
meaning: suggests that your opinions and ideas are not appreciated. Your opinions are being ignored.

context: To dream that you are in front of an audience
meaning: represents the world around you and how it is paying close attention to your actions. Alternatively, it signifies your fears of having your personal feelings and private thoughts discovered or revealed. If the audience is rowdy or noisy, then it suggests cluttered thoughts and confusion of ideas.

context: To dream that you have no audience
meaning: denotes that you are not being acknowledged for your work or achievements. Perhaps you are feeling ignored or neglected.

context: Dreaming that you are the only person in the audience
meaning: means that there is an important lesson that you and only you need to learn. Perhaps you have been oblivious to something that everyone else had already realized or notice.

context: To dream that you are at an audition
meaning: indicates feelings of insecurity and vulnerability. You have trouble expressing yourself and feel that you are being put to a test. The attitude and behavior of the audience will also guide you in how you think others perceive you.

context: To dream that you are in an auditorium
meaning: indicates that there is something that you need to learn from others. Pay attention to those around you.

context: To see an auger in your dream
meaning: signifies difficulties hard work and struggles. The dream may also have sexual connotations.

context: To dream of the month of August
meaning: suggests that there is some misunderstanding in a personal relationship or business situation.

context: To see your aunt in your dream
meaning: represents family connection, heritage and value. The aunt may also represent aspects of yourself that you like or dislike. She can also be seen as a substitute mother.

context: To see an aura around you or someone else
meaning: indicates that some important information is being relayed to you in the dream. You need to pay close attention to the message. You need to draw on this energy for strength.

context: #Ref:otoscope
meaning: #Ref:otoscope

context: To see the aurora borealis in your dream
meaning: represents renewed energy, vitality, awe, insight and youth. You will experience clarity in some situation or relationship. A positive spiritual experience will fill you with warmth and love. In addition, you will also gain some amazing new wisdom and knowledge. Alternatively, the dream indicates that you know what you need to do, but may be too lazy or too afraid to jump into action.

context: To dream about or that you are in Australia
meaning: suggests that you are being pulled toward opposite directions. The dream may also indicate self-exploration into your natural and uninhibited self. Often referred to as the land down under, the dream may be a metaphor to represent your subconscious and your underlying thoughts.

context: To see an author in your dream
meaning: suggests that your mind is preoccupied with some story, essay, or report that you are working on.

context: To dream that you are an author
meaning: indicates that you need to better express your opinions. Others are paying attention to what you have to say.

context: To dream that you or someone has autism
meaning: indicates that you are having problems communicating your feelings and thoughts to others. If you know someone with autism in real life, then the dream may be a reflection of how you are coping with this condition. It is indicative of stress.

context: To dream that you are asking for an autograph
meaning: indicates your desire to be like the person whose autograph you seek. You may be looking for some form of approval.

context: To dream that someone is asking for your autograph
meaning: suggests that you are giving your consent or approval to someone.

context: To dream of autumn
meaning: represents the cycle of life - something is about to come to an end and something new will begin. Alternatively, autumn symbolizes abundance and hospitality. It is time to collect the benefits and rewards that you've worked so hard for.

context: #Ref:car
meaning: #Ref:car

context: To see an autopsy in your dream
meaning: suggests that you are disconnected from your feelings or devoid of emotions. You need to carefully evaluate the consequences of your actions.

context: To see an avalanche in your dream
meaning: signifies your raging emotions which have been held back and repressed for a long time. These emotions have not been dealt with in a productive manner and now are being expressed in a sudden and violent anger. Alternatively, the dream symbolizes the inescapable stresses and overwhelming pressures in your life. You are feeling the weight of life's daily demands piled onto you.

context: To dream about an avatar
meaning: signifies how you want others to see you. You are putting up a front instead of being your true self.

context: #Ref:street
meaning: #Ref:street

context: To dream that you are in an aviary
meaning: indicates a decreased sense of freedom. You feel you are unable to fully express yourself.

context: To see or eat an avocado in your dream
meaning: symbolizes lust, sexuality, fertility, potential, and continuity of life. Alternatively, an avocado symbolizes richness and indulgence.

context: To see an avocado tree in your dream
meaning: suggests that you will be well rewarded if you devote some time and effort to some goal or project.

context: To dream that you are avoiding a person in your dream
meaning: suggest that you are not confronting some aspect of yourself. Consider what aspects and characteristics of the person you are avoiding which you are not recognizing in yourself. Alternatively, this word may also be a pun for "a void" in your life that you have been unable to fill.

context: To awaken in your dream
meaning: represents a spiritual rebirth. You may be acknowledging and embracing both your feminine and masculine aspects of Self. You are utilizing your fullest potential. Consider also who or what awakened you. This is an indication of what is lacking or missing in your life.

context: To dream that you awaken someone up
meaning: suggests that you are acknowledging core aspects of that person within your own self.

context: To dream that you have an awakening
meaning: signifies that new ideas will be realized. You are experiencing new awareness that is unfolding in your life.

context: Awakening
meaning: You may also be on the verge of lucid dreaming.

context: To dream that you receive an award
meaning: indicates that you feel you deserve some recognition or some acknowledgment of your work. To dream that you do not win an award symbolizes feelings of inadequacy.

context: To see an ax in your dream
meaning: indicates that you are overly controlling. It is symbolic of destruction, hostility, and the frustrations that you are experiencing. Perhaps you "have an ax to grind" with someone. Or the dream can be a metaphor that you are ready to "bury the ax" and make amends.

context: To dream that you are chopping wood with an ax
meaning: suggests that you need to divide your problems into smaller, more manageable sizes. Break down your problems into pieces you can handle. Alternatively, it indicates that your strength and power have been cut down to size.

context: To see the letter "R" in your dream
meaning: suggests that you are in need of some "R & R" or some rest and relaxation.

context: To see a rabbi in your dream
meaning: represents your attitudes about Judaism. The dream may serve to reaffirm your faith and beliefs.

context: To see a rabbit in your dream
meaning: signifies luck, magical power, and success. You have a positive outlook on life. Alternatively, rabbits symbolize abundance, warmth, fertility and sexual activity. Perhaps your sex life needs to be kept in check. The dream can also be associated with Easter time and your own personal memories of Easter.

context: In particular, to see a white rabbit in your dream
meaning: symbolizes faithfulness in love. The white rabbit also serves as a guide to steer you toward the right direction. To see a black rabbit in your dream refers to fear of intimacy.

context: If the rabbit is hopping in your dream,
meaning: then it indicates fertility. You will be surrounded by children. Alternatively, the dream may be analogous to your lack of commitment and how you jump from one thing or another.

context: If you dream that the rabbit scratches or bites you,
meaning: then it means that you need to pay more attention to your personal relationship or love life. If the bunny bites your toes, then it implies that this relationship is headed down the wrong direction.

context: To see or wear a rabbit's foot in your dream
meaning: symbolizes good luck. You are relying too much on fate and need to start taking control of your life.

context: To dream that you have rabies
meaning: represents unexpressed hostility which may erupt in violence if not expressed in a controlled manner.

context: To see a raccoon in your dream
meaning: signifies deceit and thievery. You are not being completely honest in some situation. Alternatively, the dream suggests that you are hiding something. You are keeping a secret.

context: To dream that you are in a race
meaning: represents your competitive spirit and how you tend to measure yourself against others. Alternatively, this dream may mean that you need to slow down and take a different course in life.

context: If you dream that you win a race,
meaning: then it represents your full potential and your ability to achieve your goals. You are feeling empowered and able to overcome your obstacles and those who stand in your way. The dream gives you confidence and may be a "rehearsal" for your success.

context: If you dream you lose the race,
meaning: then it indicates that you may be overextending yourself. You are setting your goals too high.

context: Dreaming of a dog race
meaning: indicates that you are looking out for your own self and your own needs. You are motivated by personal gains over community goals.

context: To see a race car in your dream
meaning: symbolizes your hard driving and headstrong attitudes. It may also reflect your competitive nature and the need to win. Alternatively, the race may be a pun for your issues with "race" and ethnicity.

context: To dream that you are driving a race car
meaning: represents your fast paced lifestyle. You may be jeopardizing your health with your reckless behavior.

context: To see a racetrack in your dream
meaning: represents life in the fast lane for you. The tracks may be a metaphor for your quest to get ahead in life. Alternatively, the dream means that you are going in circles. Or that you have a set path of thinking and doing things and are unwilling to deviate from it.

context: To experience racism in your dream
meaning: indicates that you may be too judgmental and discriminatory in some situation in your waking life. Perhaps you have falsely pre-judged someone because of the way he or she appeared.

context: To dream that you are racist
meaning: indicates your unwillingness and refusal to be cast aside. You refuse to be dismissed.

context: If you believe in racism,
meaning: then the dream is a reflection of your waking ideologies and beliefs.

context: To see an empty rack in your dream
meaning: signifies your preoccupation with a problem that has given you much anxiety. Perhaps, you are "racking" your brain for an answer to a problem.

context: To see a rack of clothes in your dream
meaning: represents your indecisiveness and self doubt. You have a lot of lingering uncertainty.

context: To dream that you are being racked
meaning: indicates that you and your actions are being called into question.

context: To hear a racket in your dream
meaning: suggests that your subconscious is desperately trying to get your attention about some matter.

context: To see or use a racquet in your dream
meaning: symbolizes your defense mechanisms. There is an issue that you are unwilling to address.

context: To see or use a radar in your dream
meaning: symbolizes your insight and intuition. The dream may be highlighting a message from your subconscious.

context: To see something radiant in your dream
meaning: indicates purity, intellectual stimulation, spiritual enlightenment and wisdom.

context: To dream that you are exposed to radiation
meaning: indicates that you are surrounded by a lot of negativity in your waking life. You are feeling overwhelmed.

context: To see a car radiator in your dream
meaning: suggests that you need to cool off. You are getting overworked.

context: To dream that you are listening to the radio
meaning: symbolizes your awareness and intuition toward a particular situation. What you hear through the radio also represents messages from your subconscious. It is possible that it is some form of ESP or telepathic communication.

context: If you dream that the radio is turned off,
meaning: then it indicates that you have the ability to help in some situation, but you are refusing to do so.

context: To dream that something is radioactive
meaning: represents suppressed emotions that are on the verge of spilling over into your conscious and creating a negative influence in your daily life. You need to address these feeling and problems before they do more harm in the long run.

context: To see or plant radishes in your garden
meaning: signify abundance and prosperity.

context: To dream that you are eating a radish
meaning: refers to some indiscretion or thoughtlessness. Perhaps the dream may be a pun on something that is "rad-dish" or coolish.

context: To dream that you are raffling an item
meaning: suggests that you need to be more giving and charitable. Alternatively, the dream is telling you to be more aware of the risks involved in leaving your destiny to fate.

context: To see a raft in your dream
meaning: indicates that you have not built a firm foundation for success. There is still much work ahead.

context: To dream that you are floating on a raft
meaning: suggests that you are drifting through life, not knowing where you are headed. You are confused about your purpose and direction in life.

context: To dream that you are white water rafting
meaning: means that you are experiencing some turbulent times.

context: To dream that you are in rage
meaning: is symbolic of your bad temper, negative outbursts, and suppressed anger. You need to express your inner strengths and desires.

context: To see old, tattered rags in your dream
meaning: indicate that you are cleaning up old problems and issues.

context: To dream that you are wearing rags
meaning: represent anxieties and concerns over your self-image. You are lacking self-esteem.

context: To dream that you are in a raid
meaning: represents your fears that some hidden aspect of your life will be discovered or made public.

context: To dream that you are holding on to a railing
meaning: suggests that you are desperately holding out for a chance to obtain the object of you affection. Alternatively, the dream indicates that you are in need of some support and assistance. Don't be afraid to ask for help.

context: To see a railroad in your dream
meaning: indicates that you have laid out a set track toward achieving your goals. Your progress will be slow but steady. You are well disciplined and secure in your life. Alternatively, the dream indicates that you may be too linear and rigid in your thinking. Perhaps a situation or relationship in your waking life has become monotonous. Sometimes you need to go off track and explore other possibilities.

context: To see an obstruction on the railroad
meaning: refers to the obstacles standing in your way toward your goals. It may also mean that you have lost track of your goals.

context: To dream that you are walking alongside the railroad tracks
meaning: signifies completion of your tasks.

context: To dream that you are crossing railroad tracks
meaning: indicates that you are going against the path that others have laid out for you. You are doing your own thing and not what others want or expect of you. Alternatively, the dream symbolizes a transitional phase. Consider the phrase of coming/being from "the wrong side of the tracks." Perhaps it signifies the progress you have made. Do not forget about your humble beginnings.

context: To see a railroad crossing gate in your dream
meaning: symbolizes temporary setbacks toward achieving your goals, especially if the gate is going down. If the gate is up, then it means that you have overcome certain obstacles in your life. You are not letting something or someone get in your way of your goals.

context: To see and hear rain falling
meaning: symbolizes forgiveness and grace. Falling rain is also a metaphor for tears, crying and sadness. Alternatively, rain symbolizes fertility and renewal. If you get wet from the rain, then it indicates cleaning from your troubles and problems. In particular, dreaming of acid rain indicates that you have been mislead. You are letting hatred and revenge take over and define you.

context: To dream that you are watching the rain from a window
meaning: indicates that spiritual ideas and insights are being brought to your awareness. It may also symbolize fortune and love.

context: To hear rain tapping on the roof
meaning: denotes spiritual ideas coming to fruition in your mind.

context: To see a rainbow in your dream
meaning: represents hope, success and good fortune in the form of money, prestige, or fame. The rainbow is also seen as a bridge between your earthly, grounded self and the higher, spiritual self. It refers to joy and happiness in your relationship. Alternatively, the rainbow implies that your troubles are almost over. Good will come out of your issues. Just hang in there. In the western culture, the rainbow is a symbol for gay pride.

context: To see an all white rainbow in your dream
meaning: signifies heightened spirituality and purity.

context: To see a rainbow at night or a lunar rainbow in your dream
meaning: is symbolic of a spiritual or emotional connection within your personal relationship or religious beliefs.

context: To dream that something is rainbow colored
meaning: implies that you need to see things in a more positive light. You need to be more optimistic. Also consider the significance of the object.

context: To dream that you have rainbow colored hair
meaning: refers to your light-hearted and carefree nature. You are headed in a positive spiritual direction.

context: To dream that you are wearing a raincoat
meaning: suggests that you are shielding yourself from your emotions. You are not able to face the nastiness. Alternatively, wearing a raincoat in your dream refers to your pessimistic outlook and unpleasantness.

context: To dream that you are in a rainforest
meaning: suggests that you feel your emotions are being undermined and "cut down". Alternatively, the dream represents your waking concerns about the environment. It may also be a metaphor of the impact that you have on your surroundings.

context: To dream that you are eating raisins
meaning: represent some negative force that is working against you. The dream may also be a metaphor for something or someone who is old and shriveled.

context: To dream that you are using a rake
meaning: indicates that some task or project will never be accomplished unless you do it yourself. Alternatively, the dream suggests that you need to have better planning and organization in your life. You need to figure out the direction you want to take in life and then carry out that plan.

context: To see someone raking in your dream
meaning: denotes that you are effectively taking advantage of some situation.

context: To see a ram in your dream
meaning: signifies aggression, energy, and impulsiveness. You may be pursuing a decision that should be approached with more tact and consideration. A ram also symbolizes strong and powerful friends who will use their influence and authority to your advantage.

context: To dream that a ram is pursuing you
meaning: indicates some misfortune or unlucky threat. Perhaps, you feel that something is being "rammed" down your throat or that you feel that you are being rammed by a situation or decision.

context: To dream that you are rambling
meaning: suggests that you have a lot that you need to get off your mind. You need to express these thoughts and feelings in your waking life or it will continue to haunt you in your dream state.

context: To dream that you are going up a ramp
meaning: signifies your struggles in achieving a goal. It is symbolic of your determination and ambition. If you fail to go up a ramp, then it suggests that you are not able to overcome your difficulties. There are still obstacles standing on your way.

context: To dream that you are going down a ramp
meaning: refers to some instability and lack of control in your life.

context: To dream that you are at a ranch
meaning: suggests that you need to take stock of your life and ascertain what you hope to achieve and gain. The dream may also refer to your own livelihood and concerns about money.

context: To dream that somebody is demanding ransom from you
meaning: suggests that you have been deceived.

context: To demand ransom in your dream
meaning: means that you are feeling unfairly treated.

context: To hear or dream that you are rapping
meaning: suggests that you need to better verbalize your thoughts and feelings.

context: To dream that you were raped or almost raped
meaning: indicates vengeful or resentful feelings toward the opposite sex. You feel that you have been violated or that you have been taken advantage of. Something or someone is jeopardizing your self-esteem and emotional well-being. Things are being forced upon you. Dreams of rape are also common for those who were actually raped in their waking life.

context: To see a rape being committed in your dream
meaning: denotes sexual dysfunction or uncertainty. In particular, if you witness a gang rape in your dream, then it signifies complete helplessness in a situation. You are lacking the resources or power to do the right thing. It may also mean that you or someone has been humiliated.

context: If you dream of raping someone,
meaning: then it represents your need to control others and show them who is in charge. You also have a sense of entitlement.

context: Dreaming that your young daughter was raped
meaning: symbolizes your fears as she grows and becomes more independent. You are learning to let go and that can't always be there to protect her.

context: To dream that you are carried away by the rapids
meaning: suggests that you are experiencing some intense feelings. You may be literally be getting carried away by your emotions.

context: To dream that you have been raptured
meaning: symbolizes your strong faith and spirituality.

context: To dream that the rapture is coming
meaning: forewarns that you need to get aspects of your life in order. Something major is happening in your life that you need to prepare for it.

context: Dreaming that you are left behind in the rapture
meaning: symbolizes feelings of abandonment and unworthiness. You may have self-esteem issues and often feel overlooked.

context: To dream that something is rare
meaning: indicates that you need to appreciate certain things. Consider the symbolism or significance of the rare object or event. Don't take things for granted.

context: To dream that you have a rash
meaning: indicates repressed anger, frustrations and annoyances. You may be holding in your anger and frustrations, instead of expressing it. Alternatively, the dream suggests that others are trying to put doubt in your head about some decision or choice that you are making. It may be a pun on a "rash" decision that you are making. You need to think twice before going through with your choice.

context: To see or eat raspberries in your dream
meaning: represent some precious or delicate matter.

context: To dream that you are rationing something
meaning: indicates that you are not getting your fair share of something, either emotionally, financially or materially. Alternatively, it symbolizes your fairness and diplomacy in some matter.

context: To see a rat in your dream
meaning: signifies feelings of doubts, greed, guilt, unworthiness and envy. You are keeping something to yourself that is eating you up inside. Or you have done something that you are not proud of. Alternatively, a rat denotes repulsion, decay, dirtiness, and even death. The dream may also be a pun on someone who is a rat. Are you feeling betrayed?

context: In particular, to see a black rat
meaning: represents deceit and covert activities. If you see a white rat in your dream, then it means that you will receive help from an unexpected source.

context: To dream that a rat is biting your feet is
meaning: analogous to the rat race that you are experiencing in your waking life.

context: To dream that you catch a rat with your bare hands
meaning: indicates that you are not letting greed, jealousy, betrayal or some other negativity get the best of you.

context: To see or play with a rattle in a dream
meaning: signifies joy, tranquility and contentment in the home.

context: To hear a rattle in your dream
meaning: represents some situation or issue that you need to tend to.

context: To see a rattlesnake in your dream
meaning: represents the passage of time.
