meaning: refers to the integration and merging of contrasting aspects of yourself. It represents psychological completion. You need to be more receptive and incorporate aspects of your dream sex partner into your own character. Consider the nature of the love-making. Was it passionate? Was it slow? Was it wild? The sex act parallels aspects of yourself that you wish to express. A more direct interpretation of the dream may be your libido's way of telling you that it has been too long since you have had sex. It may indicate repressed sexual desires and your needs for physical and emotional love. If you are looking for a place to have sex, then the dream may be analogous to your search for intimacy and closeness. You want to rekindle some relationship. If you dream of having sex in a public place, then the dream implies that others are talking about your private relationship. Dreaming of having sex on a ship refers to emotional intimacy. Perhaps the dream is telling you that you are just going through the physical aspects of sex, but are lacking the emotional connection.

context: To dream about sex with someone other than your spouse or significant other
meaning: suggests dissatisfaction with the physical side of your relationship. On the other hand, it may be harmless fantasy. In such situations, you may find that you are less inhibited sexually. Perhaps you need to bring the same sense of adventure into your existing relationship.

context: To dream that you are having sex with an ex or someone who is not your current mate
meaning: denotes your reservations about embarking in a new relationship or situation. You may feel nervous about exposing yourself and are feeling a resurgence of those old emotions and feelings that you felt back when you and your ex were together. If you are approaching your wedding date, then is not uncommon to experience especially erotic adventures with partners other than your intended spouse. This may be due to the intensity of the sexual passion with your fianc. It also relates to the new roles that you will be taking on and the uncertainty that that may bring.

context: To dream that you are having sex with a stranger
meaning: represents uncertainty about what is ahead. Alternatively, the dream allows you to experiment freely without having any hang ups, emotional baggage or preconceived notions associated with a person you would know. In such a scenario, you are able to let loose and express your desires, passions and emotions. In particular, if you dream of having sex with multiple partners at the same time, then it indicates that you are feeling detached in your personal relationship. You feel that sex is just an act devoid of any emotion or passion. Perhaps your sex life has become too automated.

context: To dream that you are having sex with a friend
meaning: refers to the closeness you share with your friend. Because you two share so much between each other and know so much about each other, the dreaming mind may depict this closeness as sex. Alternatively, such a dream indicates a level of attraction between you and your friend, but you are too afraid to act on it. Thus your desires are manifested in a dream.

context: If you are heterosexual and you dream that you are having sex with someone of the same sex,
meaning: then it represents an expression of greater self love and acceptance. You need to be in better touch of your feminine or masculine side. The dream does not necessarily imply homosexual desire.

context: To dream that you are having sex with a celebrity
meaning: indicates your drive to be successful. You are striving for recognition. Consider what movies you associate this celebrity with for clues as to where and what you want to achieve success in.

context: To dream that you are having sex with your boss
meaning: signifies your desires for authority and control. You are feeling empowered.

context: To see others having sex in your dream
meaning: refers to your own desires to be more adventurous in your own sex life.

context: To see your parents having sex in your dream
meaning: indicate that you are seeing similar aspects between their relationship and your current relationship. Most cringe at the thought of your parents having sex, so this dream imagery is really trying to get your attention. Consider your parents' real life relationship together and what you can learn from it.

context: To dream that you are the opposite sex
meaning: suggests that you need to incorporate certain qualities of the opposite sex. Ask yourself how do you feel being a man or a woman? In what ways can you incorporate those feelings into your waking life.

context: Dreaming that you are watching your girlfriend have sex with someone else
meaning: suggests that you are taking a passive role in your sex life. Maybe you feel that you are not satisfying her. The dream is signaling you to communicate your sexual concerns and/or desires. Alternatively, the dream may reflect a personal fantasy you have.

context: Dreaming that you are having sex with an alien
meaning: indicates a desire for something new and different in your sex life.

context: To dream that you are making a sex tape
meaning: means that you are sexually open to new things. You are comfortable with your sexuality. If you dream that a sex tape of you has been stolen or leaked, then it means that you are feeling over-exposed. Perhaps things are moving too fast or you are not fully comfortable in your relationship.

context: To see or use a sex toy in your dream
meaning: suggests that you are feeling unsatisfied in some area of your life, which may or may not relate to sex. There is a void in your life. Alternatively, the dream may be a play on words and that you are not taking sex seriously. Perhaps you have an immature attitude towards sex. More directly, the dream indicates your desires for a more gratifying and/or exciting sex life.

context: To see a sextant in your dream
meaning: symbolizes adventure, exploration, progress and a new journey. You are expanding your knowledge.

context: To see sextuplets in your dream
meaning: suggests that there is balance, harmony and tranquility in your family life. It also means that that you are experiencing twice as much vitality, strength and energy.

context: To dream about your own sexuality
meaning: signifies the secrets and meaning of life. You may be dealing with life issues of birth, marriage, and/or death. Alternatively, the dream suggests that you are concerned about losing your sex appeal.

context: To see a shack in your dream
meaning: represents your undeveloped self. You need to expand your Self. Alternatively, the dream may also be a pun on "shacking up".

context: To dream that you are in shackles
meaning: suggests that you are in a rut. Your daily life is becoming too much of a routine.

context: To dream that you are in the shade
meaning: symbolizes protection. There is something that you are trying to keep hidden.

context: To dream that you are shadow boxing
meaning: indicates an internal conflict. You are struggling with some moral issue or inner demons.

context: To see you own shadow in your dream
meaning: signifies an aspect of yourself which you have not acknowledged or recognized. It may be a quality about yourself or a part of you that you are rejecting or want to keep hidden. These qualities may not necessary be negative, but can be creative ones. Alternatively, the dream may mean that you are in someone else's shadow. You are constantly being overlooked and are fed up with it. In particular, if the shadow in your dream is white, then it is your subconscious' way of highlighting the shadow which is often overlooked.

context: To see a shadowy figure in your dream
meaning: represents characteristics which you have not acknowledged or incorporated into your own personality. Alternatively, it symbolizes the young, the helpless or the under-developed.

context: To dream that you are reading Shakespeare
meaning: signifies your literary aptitude. You are well-read and knowledgeable. Consider which Shakespeare novel you are reading and how the plot line may parallel a situation in your waking life.

context: To dream that you are shaking
meaning: suggests that you are getting rid of your old habits and former ways of thinking. You need to get rid of the old in order to welcome in the new and better. Shake things up a bit. Alternatively, shaking is symbolic of fear.

context: To dream of something shallow
meaning: refers to conscious knowledge and the things that you are confronting or dealing with. Alternatively, noticing that something is shallow may be a reflection of your personality. You are putting too much emphasis on physical appearances over substance.

context: To see a shaman in your dream
meaning: symbolizes a spiritual messenger or guide. The shaman is a variation of the "wise old man", an archetypal figure who represents superior knowledge, wisdom and insight. Alternatively, the dream suggests that you need to turn your negative energy into something positive.

context: To feel shame in your dream
meaning: signifies waking feelings of guilt, insecurity or low esteem that has carried over into the dream world. Perhaps you feel you have failed yourself or others.

context: To see or use shampoo in your dream
meaning: indicates that you need clear out your old attitudes and old ways of thinking. You may also need to take a different approach toward some situation or relationship. Alternatively, shampoo represents self-growth and you desire to present a new image of yourself to others.

context: To dream that you are shampooing someone else's hair
meaning: represents issues of dependency and hopelessness.

context: To see a shamrock in your dream
meaning: symbolizes your need to be or feel protected.

meaning: suggests that things in your life may literally be taking shape. You have a clearer understanding of things. Consult the specific shapes for additional meaning.

The shark may also be an aspect of your own personality with these qualities.

meaning: then it means that you are emotionally vulnerable. You are trying to suppress your anger, but it is just too much to keep in.

If you dream of a warship, then it means that you are experiencing feelings of aggression. If you dream of a pirate ship, then it signifies your suppressed desires for freedom and adventure. Dreaming of a tanker ship implies that you are keeping your true feelings inside.

meaning: denotes that you are still standing tall despite the emotional turmoil occurring in your life.

meaning: suggests that you are experiencing some emotional conflict or are having difficulties in expressing your feelings. Additionally, the dream means that you are you ready to confront some issues in your subconscious.

meaning: suggest that you are getting ready for a challenge. Or you are ready to move forward with your goals or a decision.

If you are changing your shoes, then it refers to your changing roles. You are taking a new approach to life. If you forget your shoes, then it suggests that you are leaving behind your inhibitions. context: Dreaming that you are wearing mismatched shoes

context: To see or shoot a shotgun in your dream

If you were swimming on the deep end, then it means that those emotions are deeply seated and may be harder to confront. You will need to work through it, no more matter how difficult. meaning: implies that you are desperate to escape from a situation.

context: To dream that you reach out to touch a ghost, but it disappears
meaning: indicates that you are taking steps to acknowledging some painful or repressed thoughts even though you are not ready to fully confront them.

context: To see the ghost of a living relative or friend in your dream
meaning: signifies that you are in danger of malice acts by that person.

context: To see the ghost of a dead friend/relative in your dream
meaning: suggests guilt and regrets concerning the past relationships with that particular person.

context: To dream that ghosts are trying to kill you
meaning: implies that you are ready to confront your past and your repressed emotions, despite how painful it may be. You are ready to move forward with your life and leave the past behind. If a ghost is choking you in your dream, then it means that some past situation is preventing you from fully expressing yourself.

context: Dreaming that you are being stalked or haunted by a ghost
meaning: indicates that you are refusing to confront issues from your past which is affecting your present life.

context: To dream that you are in a ghost town
meaning: suggests that you are feeling rejected by society. You may be isolating yourself from others. Alternatively, the dream means that you are living in the past and clinging onto memories. It is time to let go and live in the present times.

context: To see a ghoul in your dream
meaning: suggests that your habits and negative ways are hindering your growth. The dream may also represent a fresh beginning.

context: To see a giant in your dream
meaning: indicates a great struggle between you and your opponents. You are trying to overcome an overwhelming obstacle. Alternatively, a giant symbolizes an issue, a person or a feeling that is dominating you. You are having an inferiority complex.

context: To dream that you turn into a giant
meaning: indicates feelings of inferiority.

context: To dream that you are giving a gift
meaning: signifies your generosity towards others. Alternatively, you may be trying to express some feeling or have something awkward to say that has to be carefully packaged. If you are showering someone with gifts, then it indicates that you are being overly pushy with your advice. Or that you are trying too hard to be accepted. If you are buying or giving someone expensive gifts, then it symbolizes the sacrifices you are making for that person. You want to make them feel important.

context: To dream that you receive a gift
meaning: indicates that you are being rewarded and recognized for your generosity and giving nature. You are held in high esteem by those around you. If someone gives you an inappropriate gift, then it suggests that you are the subject of unwelcome attention from someone. If you dream that you give someone an inappropriate gift, then it suggests that your true nature will eventually be exposed. Analyze the gift you give or receive for additional significance.

context: To see a pile of gifts
meaning: symbolizes unutilized or unrecognized skills and talents.

context: To open a gift and find something disgusting inside
meaning: symbolizes disappointments or unexpected failures.

context: To see a gift card in your dream
meaning: means that there is something you didn't realize you needed or that there is something missing from your life. Ask yourself which store the gift card is for and how it relates to something you may be lacking.

context: To see gift wrap in your dream
meaning: suggests that there is something that you are trying to cover up or hide. You are trying to present something unpleasant in a more inviting or cheerful manner. Consider what you are wrapping, as well as the color, pattern and occasion of the wrapping paper for additional significance. Alternatively, the dream symbolizes celebration and happiness. You are acknowledging a special occasion.

context: To dream of playing at a gig
meaning: represents a freedom of expression and the ability to let go of the confines in your daily life.

context: To dream that you have gills
meaning: implies that you are ready to confront your true feelings and submerge yourself in your emotions.

context: To see ginger in your dream
meaning: indicates security and comfort in your life. However, you need to add a little more excitement and variety to you life.

context: To see or eat gingerbread in your dream
meaning: refers to homeliness and the comforts of home. You are in a happy place. In particular. to see a gingerbread man signifies family togetherness and joy.

context: To see ginseng in your dream
meaning: represents virility, longevity and life.

context: To see a giraffe in your dream
meaning: suggests that you need to consider the overall picture. Take a broader view on your life and where it is headed. The dream may also be a metaphor on how you are "sticking your neck out" for someone.

context: To dream that you are riding a giraffe
meaning: represents your desire to stand up amongst the crowd. You want attention, but aren't getting it.

context: To dream that a giraffe is running
meaning: implies that you are avoiding the truth. It also suggests that you saw something that you shouldn't have seen.

context: To dream that you are wearing a girdle
meaning: suggests that you are feeling restricted and limited in the expression of your ideas and feelings. Alternatively, the dream points to your tendency to bear pain in order to please others.

context: To dream that you are a girl scout
meaning: symbolizes sisterhood, camaraderie, characters and strong values. You need to exemplify these qualities.

context: To see a girl scout in your dream
meaning: suggests that you need to be more dedicated to your goals and achievements. Alternatively, a girl scout may represent model behavior which you are trying to emulate.

context: To see your girlfriend in your dream
meaning: represents your waking relationship with her and how you feel about her.

context: To dream that you are pretending to be someone's girlfriend
meaning: implies that you are not ready to settle down into a committed relationship. You don't want to be tied down.

context: To dream that you are meeting your girlfriend's parents is a rehearsal for the actual meeting. You
meaning: may be nervous about meeting them and it's probably been weighing on your mind. If you have already meet your girlfriend's parents and dream of meeting them again, then the dream is a reminder for you to be on your best behavior. You tend to be more on your toes when it comes to someone else's parents.

context: Dreaming that you are watching your girlfriend have sex with someone else
meaning: suggests that you are taking a passive role in your sex life. Maybe you feel that you are not satisfying her. The dream is signaling you to communicate your sexual concerns and/or desires. Alternatively, the dream may reflect a personal fantasy you have.

context: To see a girl in your dream
meaning: represents your playful, innocent, and childlike nature. Perhaps you are behaving immaturely in some situation. Alternatively, a girl represents the feminine qualities of your character.

context: To dream about a girl that you just met
meaning: represents your anxieties and thoughts of whether you had made a good impression on her and what she thought of you. If she told you that she disliked you in the dream, then it may be an excuse for you to dismiss her and not pursue a relationship further.

context: To dream that you are giving something away
meaning: indicates that you need to give more in some relationship or situation. To be able to give helps fulfill your need to share and to belong. Consider also how you were received.

context: To dream that something is given to you
meaning: suggests that you need to appreciate the gifts you have.

context: To see or eat gizzards in your dream
meaning: refers to a difficult or emotional situation that you are trying to process and understand.

context: To see a glacier in your dream
meaning: refers to your cold feelings. You are shutting down emotionally. Alternatively, glaciers denote evitable changes.

context: To dream that you are a gladiator
meaning: represents a situation where you are fighting for your survival. You feel that others are working against you. Alternatively, the dream means that you are confronting issues from your subconscious.

context: To see gladiolas in your dream
meaning: represent heartaches and issues of the heart. It serves to remind you that sometimes love hurts.

context: To see glass in your dream
meaning: symbolizes passivity or protection. You may be putting up an invisible barrier to protect yourself in a situation or relationship. If the glass is dirty, cloudy or discolored, then it suggests that you are not seeing something clearly. You need more clarity in a situation. To dream that you are drinking from a glass is an omen of good luck.

context: To dream that you are looking through glass
meaning: represents your openness and non-defensiveness. Alternatively, you may be putting up an invisible emotional barrier around yourself.

context: To see broken glass in your dream
meaning: signifies disappointments and negative changes in your life. Alternatively, it could be symbolic of an aspect of your life that is in pieces. A relationship or situation has come to an abrupt and untimely end. If you are walking on broken glass, then it suggests that you will be experiencing some heartache or pain. You are unsure with how to proceed with your life.

context: Dreaming of glass suddenly shattering
meaning: symbolizes a major breakthrough in some area of your life. You have overcome some obstacle.

context: To dream that you are eating glass
meaning: highlights your vulnerability, confusion and frailty. You may have difficulties in communicating your thoughts across and getting the right words out. Alternatively, it may symbolize your hurtful and cutting comments. Perhaps you have been hurt or disappointed by something that someone had said. Or you need to be careful in how you phrase and word things or run the risk of offending others.

context: To see a glass case in your dream
meaning: implies that you are distancing yourself emotionally from some situation or relationship. You are guarded about your feelings. Consider the significance of what is inside the glass case. Alternatively, the dream symbolizes a cherished memory.

context: To see a glass house in your dream
meaning: suggests that you need to be cautious about what people are telling you. They may be telling you what you want to hear, and not necessarily what you need to hear.

context: To dream that you are living in a glass house
meaning: signifies a threat to your reputation. It may also suggest that you are being watched or are under scrutiny. Consider the proverb of how people who live in glass houses shouldn't throw stones. In other words, the dream may be advising you not to criticize others, especially if you are also guilty of those same faults. You need to be more accepting.

context: To see or wear glass slippers in your dream
meaning: symbolize truth and transformation.

context: To see a glassblower in your dream
meaning: represents your ability to mold and shape the lives around you.

context: To see a drinking glass in your dream
meaning: signifies healing, rejuvenation, and healing. Alternatively, it indicates a transcendence into a realm of higher consciousness. Is the glass half-full or half-empty? Do you see life from an optimistic or pessimistic point of view. Consider also the contents of the glass. If you are drinking from a glass, then it is a positive omen.

context: To see a broken glass in your dream
meaning: denotes feelings of powerlessness, guilt and/or low self-esteem. Perhaps you feel unqualified or inadequate in dealing with a situation. You believe others can see your shortcomings or insecurities.

context: To dream that you are washing glassware or drinking glasses
meaning: suggests that you are looking for clarity in a situation.

context: Dreaming that you throw a drinking glass on the ground and it doesn't break as expected
meaning: refers to your resilience and your ability bounce back from hardship. You or someone is not as fragile as you had thought.

context: To see or ride a glider in your dream
meaning: represents your tendency to go with the flow of things instead of taking your own initiative and making changes in your life. It may also mean that things are a breeze for you.

context: To see or throw glitter in your dream
meaning: suggests that you need to be more outgoing. Express yourself! The dream may also be a metaphor for fame, glitz, and glamour, as in the glitter of Hollywood.

context: To dream that something is glittering
meaning: indicates that something or someone is trying to get your attention. Alternatively, the dream may indicate that things are not always what it seems. Consider the phrase "all that glitters is not gold." Don't be fooled by what is on the outside or how things may appear to be.

context: To see a globe in your dream
meaning: suggests that you need to step back and look at the wider perspective. It also indicates that you are in complete control of your life.

context: To see a spinning globe in your dream
meaning: signifies that your life is going out of control.

context: To be surrounded by gloomy things and situations in your dream
meaning: indicates that you need some direction or clarity in a waking situation. A situation or person in your life is having a negative impact on you.

context: To see or wear gloves in your dream
meaning: represent the way you handle things. You are getting a handle on a problem. Consider the phrase "handle with kid gloves" and how you need to be more cautious in some situation. Or perhaps you are overly cautious. Alternatively, wearing gloves may mean that your creative abilities are still latent. You need to acknowledge and express that creative side.

context: To dream that you are taking off gloves
meaning: symbolize respect.

context: To dream that you are wearing work gloves
meaning: represent a difficult situation that may get your hands dirty. If you are wearing driving gloves, then it means that you need to take control of your life. If you are wearing boxing gloves, that it indicate that you are involved in a some sort of conflict. Is there something in your life that you are struggling with? To wear white gloves in your dream signify luxury and richness.

context: To dream that you throw a glove on the floor
meaning: suggests that you need to challenge or address someone about an issue that is bothering you.

context: To see a glow in your dream
meaning: symbolizes enlightenment and understanding. New light has been shed onto a situation. You have gained a fresh perspective.

context: To dream that a person is glowing
meaning: means that you finally understand this person in a new way. Alternatively, a person who is glowing represents someone who is offering their guidance and support.

context: To see a glow stick in your dream
meaning: indicates a new direction that you are taking. You may also be seeking some guidance in the course of your actions.

context: To see glue in your dream
meaning: indicates a fear of being trapped in some situation and not being able to get out of it. You have a fear of partnership or commitment and a general distrust of people around you. On the flip side, you may be too clingy. Alternatively, you are holding on to some false hope.

context: To dream that you are gluing something together
meaning: suggests that you are piecing together aspects of yourself and acknowledging those previously rejected parts. Alternatively, the dream may be a metaphor for a sticky situation.

context: To see a gnat in your dream
meaning: signifies some nagging or annoying issue. Alternatively, it represents that a sweet opportunity is nearby.

context: To dream that you are gnawing at something
meaning: suggests that you are trying to attack or confront a situation or problem that has been menacing you. The dream may also be a metaphor to mean "nah" or "no".

context: To see a gnome in your dream
meaning: signifies the inner child and its fantasies. Alternatively, a gnome represents protection, luck, fruitfulness and fertility.

context: To see a gnu in your dream
meaning: indicates a lack of control in your life. You are letting your bitter feelings and negative emotions get the best of you. Alternatively, a gnu may be a pun on "knew". The dream may be telling you that you already hold the truth.

context: To see or drive a go-kart in your dream
meaning: represents your ability to navigate through life's twists and turns. The dream may also be a pun on your "drive" and ambition.

context: To score a goal in your dream
meaning: symbolizes your achievements and successes. Your path to success is within reach. The dream may also be a metaphor for the goals you have in your life. Or it may suggests that you need to start making goals for your future.

context: To miss a goal in your dream
meaning: indicates that you are not utilizing all your resources to achieve your goals. You need to reevaluate your choices.

context: To see a goal post in your dream
meaning: symbolizes your personal goals or an opportunity that is within your grasp. Alternatively, the dream means that you need to be more receptive to some idea or notion.

context: To see or dream that you are a goalie
meaning: represents your capabilities and your ability to achieve. You are feeling confident and empowered.

context: To see a goat in your dream
meaning: represents your lack of judgment and your gullibility. Alternatively, goats are symbolic of sexuality, sexual desire, and lechery. Also consider the associations with the goat as in "scapegoat" or "getting someone's goat". Do you feel that you have been blamed for someone else's deed?

context: To dream that a billy goat butts you
meaning: forewarns of deceit, underhandedness, and lies.

context: To see someone with a goatee in your dream
meaning: represents mistrust and dishonesty.

context: Dreaming that you have a goatee
meaning: means that you need to approach a problem via unconventional methods. Think outside the box. The dream may also be telling you to go against the crowd.

context: To see or drink from a goblet in your dream

context: To see a goblin in your dream
meaning: refers to a negative person who is working against you. Or it may mean that you have a self-defeatist attitude. You are already setting yourself up for failure.

context: To see God in your dream
meaning: signifies your spirituality and expression of your feelings about divinity. God also symbolizes an untouchable, unreachable, and unattainable notion of perfection. Thus such a dream may highlight your struggles and attempts with trying to be perfect.

context: To dream that you are worshipping God
meaning: signifies repentance of your actions and errors.

context: To dream that God speaks to you
meaning: signifies feelings of guilt, eternal punishment, and damnation.

context: To dream that you are a god
meaning: implies your own special talents which you have not yet recognized or fully developed. Alternatively, it refers to your feelings of superiority over others. You think you are above others and have a tendency to look down on people.

context: To dream that God has the bluest eyes
meaning: refers to your deep and intimate connection with God. Through his eyes, you also see his wisdom and devotion. He is your spiritual guide.

context: To see a goddess in your dream
meaning: symbolizes your femininity or feminine side. For a man to dream of a goddess indicates his fears about the female.

context: To see your godfather in your dream
meaning: signifies a fear for authority. If you have a godfather in real life, then it is important to consider your personal relationship with him.

context: To dream that you are a godfather
meaning: indicates that you are an authority figure. Someone is looking to you for advice.

context: To see your godmother in your dream
meaning: indicates that you are looking for advice and direction in life.

context: To dream that you have a fairy godmother
meaning: refers to your need to feel protected. Perhaps you are unsure about a decision you are making.

context: To see Godzilla in your dream
meaning: signifies feelings of being out of control. A certain situation is getting the best of you.

context: To see or wear goggles in your dream
meaning: suggest that you are trying to protect yourself from emotional harm. Perhaps you need to confront something in your waking like that you know is hurting you.

context: To dream that you have a goiter
meaning: indicates that you are overlooking some minor issue that will have significant consequences. Alternatively, a goiter represents a situation that you are having difficulty confronting or accepting.

context: To see gold in your dream
meaning: symbolizes wealth, riches, natural healing, illumination and/or spirituality. It is also a symbol of love, longevity and domestic bliss. Negatively, gold may represent greed, corruption and temptation.

context: To find gold in your dream
meaning: indicates that you have discovered something valuable about yourself. This may be some hidden talent or knowledge.

context: To bury gold in your dream
meaning: suggests that you are trying to hide something about yourself.

context: To dream that you are a gold digger
meaning: implies that you have an extremely high sense of self worth.

context: Dreaming that someone is a gold digger
meaning: indicates that you are reevaluating your own path to success.

context: To see gold leaves in your dream
meaning: indicates a pleasant and bright future ahead for you.

context: To see the Golden Gate Bridge in your dream
meaning: signifies hope, possibilities and activism. The Golden Gate Bridge is also an indication that you are going through an important transition.

context: To see a golden retriever in your dream
meaning: represents your family ideals. The dream may also be a pun on something that you need to "retrieve" or regain control of.

context: To see a goldenrod in your dream
meaning: indicates that something or someone is causing you much annoyance and irritation.

context: To see a goldfinch in your dream
meaning: symbolizes your soul. It is also an indication of the sacrifices you have made.

context: To see a goldfish in your dream signifies, wealth, success, and pleasant adventures.
meaning: Alternatively, goldfish represents some important emotional matter or valuable insight.

context: To dream that you are playing or watching golf
meaning: signifies pleasant indulgences. It may also indicate that you are idling and wasting time. Alternatively, the dream symbolizes your individual accomplishments and your drive to succeed.

context: To dream that you are on a golf course
meaning: represents your desires for freedom. You want to escape the grind of your occupation. Alternatively, the dream may be a pun of how you are green or environmentally conscious.

context: Dreaming that you are attending a golf tournament
meaning: indicates that you are not getting the full picture. You are only seeing what you want to see.

context: To see a golf ball in your dream
meaning: symbolizes a frivolous matter or situation. Don't let the small things get to you.

context: To see or ride a golf cart in your dream
meaning: suggests that you are too lackadaisical in the pursuit of your goals. You have no sense of urgency in things.

context: To see or hold a golf club in your dream
meaning: symbolizes your drive, energy and determination. These are the qualities that you need to achieve your goals.

context: Dreaming of a bag of golf clubs
meaning: highlights exclusivity, wealth and prestige.

context: To see or use a golf tee in your dream
meaning: refers to your supporting role in a situation. Don't underestimate your abilities and what you can offer to a situation.

context: To see or ride in a gondola in your dream
meaning: refers to romance, fantasy, and idealistic love. Things are going well in your relationship or some aspect of your waking life. Alternatively, a gondola indicates your need to take time off and go off on an adventure.

meaning: indicates an end to your worries, to a relationship or and to a chapter in your life. You are moving on into a new stage of your life.

context: To dream that someone is saying goodbye to you
meaning: suggests that you are going on a journey of self-discovery. You are entering a new phase in your life.

context: To dream that you have your own goons or that you are surrounded or chased by goons
meaning: mean that there is an issue that you are avoiding. You have unresolved inner conflicts and are refusing to address certain issues or feelings directly.

context: To see a goose in your dream
meaning: symbolizes fertility and motherly love. The goose may also represent a message from your subconscious. Alternatively, the dream suggests that you are on a "wild goose chase". Perhaps you are going about a problem all wrong.

context: To dream that you have a goose egg on your head
meaning: means that you are acting impulsively. You are not thinking through the consequences of your action.

context: To dream that you have goosebumps
meaning: indicate validity and truth to what you have just said or heard. Alternatively, it may symbolize fear and/or your frigid attitude.

context: To pick or gather gooseberries in your dream
meaning: signify a happy and bright outlook. You have successfully overcome your problems.

context: To see or eat gooseberries in your dream
meaning: suggest that you are enjoying your time of leisure.

context: To see a gopher in your dream
meaning: means that you are being used and manipulated by others. Alternatively, the dream may be a pun on "go for" it. You need to take initiative and act now.

context: To see a gorilla in your dream
meaning: suggests that you may be too "over the top" in your behavior. Perhaps you are compensating for your rigidity and stiffness in your waking life. Alternatively, the gorilla symbolizes your primitive impulses, wild nature and repressed sexual energy.

context: To dream that you are gossiping
meaning: suggests that you are engaging in counterproductive activity.

context: To hear gossip in your dream
meaning: indicates that you are using others to get information that may not be accurate.

context: If you are not goth in waking life, but dream that you or someone is goth,
meaning: then it refers to something that you are still trying to understand. Perhaps it is your feelings that you are trying to understand. Alternatively, the dream implies that you are going against the masses and expressing your own personal freedom.

context: To see a gourd in your dream
meaning: represents abundance, longevity and fertility. It is also a feminine symbol denoting the womb.

context: To dream you have gout
meaning: represents obstacles. Something may be hindering or slowing your progress.

meaning: signifies power and the qualities or feelings that rule your life. Do greed, lust, or love guide you in how you live? The dream may also reflect your views about society at large.

If the gown is plain or simple, then it suggests a simplified lifestyle. Alternatively, to dream you are wearing an evening gown indicates that you are looking for happiness.

context: To dream that you are using a GPS
meaning: indicates that you are on a path of self discovery. It symbolizes your goal and purpose in life.

context: To see your grade in your dream
meaning: represents how well you are doing in life's lesson and how your are progressing through each stage in your life. Consider the significance of the letter. Perhaps it refers to someone's initials.

context: To dream that you do not have enough units or credits to graduate
meaning: suggests that you are not giving yourself enough credit to your successes and achievements. You are short-changing yourself of your accomplishments.

context: To dream that you forget your graduation
meaning: means that you are not mentally prepared for the next phase of your life. You are subconsciously trying to hold yourself back.

context: To see graffiti in your dream
meaning: indicates that you have low self-worth. If the graffiti in your dream is a positive symbol, then it suggests that you see the good in everything and everyone.

meaning: indicates that you are making connections and bonds. You may be bringing together two different things that would better exist apart.

context: To see grains your dream
meaning: signify abundance, wealth, fertility, growth and happiness. It also represents all the hard work that you have done and completed.

context: To dream that you are studying grammar
meaning: suggests difficulties in getting your point across and communicating your ideas.

meaning: represents the renewal of life and reflection of your own past. It refers to your family line, generations and tradition, as well as innocence and purity. Alternatively, you may be expressing a desire to escape from your daily responsibilities and problems.

meaning: symbolizes tradition, protection, wisdom, and a caring nature. Consider the qualities and characteristics that exist in your own grandfather.

context: If your grandfather is dead and you dream that he is alive,
meaning: then it may just mean that you miss them and are trying to relive the time you spent with them when he was alive. If you dream that your grandfather is doing odd things, then it implies that you are still trying to understand his death. Perhaps you haven't come to terms with why he passed away.

context: To see a grandfather clock in your dream
meaning: signifies the past or a passage of time. Perhaps a decision has been weighing on your mind for quite some time. Alternatively, a grandfather clock may refer to the patriarch and perhaps some outdated views and way of thinking.

context: To see your grandmother in your dream
meaning: represents nurturance, protection, and unconditional love. Consider the qualities and characteristics that exist in your own grandmother. She may also be the archetypal symbol of the wise old woman.

context: To see your grandparents in your dream
meaning: symbolize love, security, wisdom and protection.

context: To dream that you are searching for your grandparents
meaning: signify your search for love and protection. You may be regressing to childhood needs.

context: To dream of your grandparents' home
meaning: refers to longevity, security and good old fashion values. You need to lay a solid foundation in order to grow. Obviously, your own personal associations with your grandparents' home will factory strongly into its significance. What did you do while you were at your grandparents? What sort of memories did you have? What did you do when you visited your grandparents?

context: To dream that you are in the grandstands
meaning: represents your goals and your plans on how to achieve them. Alternatively, dreaming of being in the grandstands indicate that you are seeking praise and attention from others. Or that you are trying to hard to impress others.

context: To see granite in your dream
meaning: refers to your toughness and rigidity. You tend to be unyielding and inflexible in your thinking.

context: To see or eat a grapefruit in your dream
meaning: represents a sense of well-being and a refreshed state of mind. Your are experiencing an uplift in your spirits and a rejuvenation of your body.

context: To see a grapefruit tree in your dream
meaning: is symbolic of your talents, belief system and good deeds. It may also represent the fruits of your labor.

context: To see grape vines in your dream
meaning: symbolize opulence, wealth, and decadence. It also indicates fortitude and your ability to offer happiness to others.

context: To see or eat grapes in your dream
meaning: represent wealth and prosperity. In the end, your hard work will pay off and you will be rewarded for your labor. Alternatively, grapes refer to immortality and sacrifices.

context: To dream that you are picking and gathering grapes
meaning: signify profit and the realization of your desires.

context: To see or use a grappling hook in your dream
meaning: refers to something that is just beyond your grasp. Sometimes you need the support of those around you to help you achieve your goals. Alternatively, a grappling hook indicates that you are overextending yourself or overstepping your boundaries.

meaning: suggests that there is a part of yourself that you can always rely on. The dream is also symbolic of natural protection. Also consider the phrase "the grass is always greener on the other side." Do you always compare yourself with others and look at what other people have?

context: To dream that you are planting grass
meaning: indicates that your hard work and efforts will pay off in the end.

context: Dreaming that there is grass in your mouth or that you are eating grass
meaning: represents a situation that you have a difficult time accepting or an emotion that you don't want to acknowledge.

context: To see a grasshopper in your dream
meaning: symbolizes freedom, independence or spiritual enlightenment. Alternatively, it indicates your inability to settle down or commit to a decision.

context: To see or dream that you are on a grassland
meaning: symbolizes openness and concealment at the same time. You need to learn to balance when to reveal information about yourself and when to hold back.

context: To see or use a grater in your dream
meaning: implies that you need to process things in smaller sizes so that you do not get overwhelmed. Alternatively, the dream is a pun on "great" or "greater". The dream may be telling you that big things are in store for you.

context: To dream that you are at a grave

The dream may also be a pun on feeling grave or concerns about a serious or sad situation.

context: To dream that you are digging a grave
meaning: denotes some nervousness and uneasiness over some undertaking.

context: To dream that your dead uncle calls to tell you that he is digging graves
meaning: indicates that your subconscious is telling you about some hidden truth or family secret that needs to be uncovered.

context: To see gravel in your dream
meaning: signifies practicality.
